WEBVTT

00:01.936 --> 00:04.672
[male voice in alien language]

00:11.779 --> 00:13.781
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

00:52.119 --> 00:56.658
[Irulan]
<i>Diary ya Imperial. Mwaka 10,191.</i>
<i>Third comment.</i>

00:59.794 --> 01:03.430
<i>The battle for Arrakis</i>
<i>took everyone by surprise.</i>

01:04.566 --> 01:05.667
<i>There were no witnesses.</i>

01:05.700 --> 01:07.669
[somber music playing]

01:07.702 --> 01:10.805
<i>The Harkonnen operation</i>
<i>was perpetrated overnight,</i>

01:10.838 --> 01:14.709
<i>without warning</i>
<i>or declaration of war.</i>

01:16.878 --> 01:19.413
<i>By morning,</i>
<i>the Atreides were no more.</i>

01:21.148 --> 01:22.316
<i>All died in the dark.</i>

01:31.325 --> 01:32.794
<i>And the Emperor said...</i>

01:36.363 --> 01:37.230
<i>nothing.</i>

01:39.801 --> 01:42.302
<i>Since that night, my father</i>
<i>has not been the same.</i>

01:43.605 --> 01:44.505
<i>Nor have I.</i>

01:46.406 --> 01:49.811
<i>His inaction</i>
<i>is difficult for me to accept.</i>

01:49.844 --> 01:52.747
<i>Kwa, I know he loved</i>
<i>Duke Leto Atreides like a son.</i>

01:55.282 --> 01:56.884
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

01:56.918 --> 01:59.219
[chain clanks]

01:59.252 --> 02:00.922
[Irulan] <i>But my father's</i>
<i>always been guided</i>

02:00.955 --> 02:05.325
<i>by the calculus of power.</i>

02:05.359 --> 02:08.328
<i>This would not be</i>
<i>the first time the Harkonnens</i>
<i>have done his dirty work.</i>

02:10.865 --> 02:12.667
[shouts in Harkonnen]

02:12.700 --> 02:14.267
[Harkonnen army shouts]

02:16.871 --> 02:19.406
In the shadows of Arrakis
lie many secrets...

02:21.876 --> 02:24.277
<i>but the darkest yam all</i>
<i>may remain.</i>

02:25.880 --> 02:27.615
<i>The end of Nyumba ya Atreides.</i>

02:32.319 --> 02:35.322
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

02:43.665 --> 02:46.868
[Paulo] <i>Sister, Father amekufa.</i>

02:48.503 --> 02:50.303
<i>Shouldn't you go back</i>
<i>to the stars,</i>

02:51.304 --> 02:52.172
<i>be with him?</i>

02:54.742 --> 02:57.912
<i>I'm afraid I won't have</i>
<i>enough time to fix things</i>
<i>before your coming.</i>

03:00.480 --> 03:02.717
<i>This world is beyond cruelty.</i>

03:07.989 --> 03:10.892
[anapumua sana]

03:14.529 --> 03:16.263
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

03:20.601 --> 03:22.503
[shusha]

03:39.020 --> 03:40.387
[kutia saini]

03:43.323 --> 03:44.859
[Askari wa Harkonnen 1
akizungumza Harkonnen]

03:44.892 --> 03:46.460
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

03:52.800 --> 03:54.936
[Fremen panting]

03:58.438 --> 04:00.273
[Askari wa Harkonnen 1
continues akizungumza Harkonnen]

04:03.911 --> 04:06.379
[Stilgar breathes heavily]

04:09.550 --> 04:10.985
Stay here.

04:11.018 --> 04:14.522
[mimicking bird]

04:29.737 --> 04:31.806
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

04:38.045 --> 04:39.479
[kutia saini]

04:40.347 --> 04:41.949
[Jessica panting]

04:47.454 --> 04:48.623
[Jessica grunts]

04:51.659 --> 04:53.961
[wote wawili wakihema]

04:55.462 --> 04:57.632
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

04:57.665 --> 04:59.432
[wote wawili wakihema]

05:02.770 --> 05:04.705
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

05:09.911 --> 05:12.079
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

05:30.531 --> 05:34.434
[Harkonnen squad leader
kupumua sana]

05:34.467 --> 05:36.103
[akizungumza Harkonnen]

05:59.560 --> 06:00.427
[Paulo anaguna]

06:05.099 --> 06:05.933
[anaongea Harkonnen]

06:08.636 --> 06:10.137
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

06:11.438 --> 06:12.139
[anapumua sana]

06:14.709 --> 06:17.011
[anapumua sana]

06:17.044 --> 06:19.046
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

06:19.080 --> 06:21.148
[Harkonnen squad leader
akizungumza Harkonnen]

06:28.055 --> 06:29.924
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

07:07.728 --> 07:08.696
[explodes]

07:09.830 --> 07:12.166
[high frequency whirring]

07:13.801 --> 07:15.503
[akizungumza Harkonnen]

07:15.536 --> 07:16.871
[kupumua sana]

07:16.904 --> 07:19.106
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

07:29.250 --> 07:30.618
[akizungumza Harkonnen]

07:30.651 --> 07:31.519
[bang]

07:34.889 --> 07:36.991
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

07:37.024 --> 07:42.096
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

07:45.066 --> 07:46.734
[Paulo gasps, pants]

07:46.767 --> 07:48.235
[Askari wa Harkonnen
shouting in Harkonnen]

07:48.269 --> 07:50.171
[shots fired]

07:50.204 --> 07:52.840
[Paulo na Jessica grunt, pant]

07:56.544 --> 07:58.212
[Harkonnen lieutenant
akizungumza Harkonnen]

08:10.324 --> 08:11.525
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

08:14.028 --> 08:16.097
[Paulo panting]

08:18.733 --> 08:20.067
[Paulo anaguna]

08:21.002 --> 08:24.772
[both shouting, grunting]

08:29.844 --> 08:30.711
[Paulo anaguna]

08:33.080 --> 08:34.849
[kuhema]

08:40.821 --> 08:42.056
[high pitched whirring]

08:42.089 --> 08:43.724
[Harkonnen sniper
akizungumza Harkonnen]

08:43.758 --> 08:44.892
[Jessica na Harkonnen sniper
grunt]

08:45.960 --> 08:50.331
[Jessica shouts, grunts]

08:50.364 --> 08:51.899
[Harkonnen sniper grunts]

08:51.932 --> 08:53.734
[Jessica panting]

08:57.371 --> 09:00.141
[kuhema]

09:00.174 --> 09:03.611
Never stna with your back
towards the open.

09:03.644 --> 09:05.279
How many times do I have
to tell you that, huh?

09:05.312 --> 09:07.681
-[wote wawili wakihema]
-[Paulo] You okay?

09:07.715 --> 09:09.950
-Yeah.
-How 'bout her?

09:12.019 --> 09:12.987
She's fine.

09:15.990 --> 09:17.858
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

09:19.326 --> 09:23.764
[kuguna] They do not usually
venture this deep.

09:23.798 --> 09:25.633
They wanna make sure
no Atreides escaped.

09:25.666 --> 09:28.102
[Stilgar chuckles]
You think too much of yourself.

09:28.135 --> 09:30.871
No, no,
we are in the deep desert.

09:30.905 --> 09:33.741
Only Fremen can survive here.

09:33.774 --> 09:36.110
They were here for us,
not for you.

09:36.143 --> 09:39.080
[anacheka] Don't worry.

09:39.113 --> 09:42.183
I'm taking you somewhere
they will never find us.

09:42.216 --> 09:44.251
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]
[kushangaza]

09:59.433 --> 10:01.635
Filthy water.

10:01.669 --> 10:05.739
It's full of chemicals,
but good enough
for cooling systems.

10:06.874 --> 10:08.075
[Jessica gags]

10:09.777 --> 10:10.744
Don't let it out.

10:10.778 --> 10:13.013
-[sloshing]
-[ejects]

10:13.047 --> 10:15.182
-You okay?
-Mm-hmm.

10:15.216 --> 10:16.383
Don't let that out.

10:16.417 --> 10:18.752
-[gags]
-Don't let it out!

10:18.786 --> 10:20.988
-[Jessica vomits]
-[anaongea Chakobsa]

10:21.021 --> 10:23.023
[Jessica breathes heavily]

10:23.057 --> 10:24.158
-[Jessica] I'm okay.
-[Paulo] Je, una uhakika?

10:24.191 --> 10:25.092
Mm-hmm.

10:25.126 --> 10:26.727
[anapumua kwa kina]

10:29.797 --> 10:30.931
You fought well...

10:31.999 --> 10:33.167
once you woke up.

10:34.435 --> 10:35.336
I wasn't sleeping.

10:35.369 --> 10:36.770
[anadhihaki]

10:38.372 --> 10:42.409
[Askari wa Harkonnen grunts,
chokes]

10:45.980 --> 10:47.214
[Stilgar mimics bird]

10:47.248 --> 10:50.017
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

10:50.050 --> 10:51.418
[Stilgar clicks tongue]

10:52.887 --> 10:55.055
[kuzungumza bila kujulikana]

10:57.491 --> 10:59.994
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

11:06.934 --> 11:08.936
[Paulo] No, no, no. I'll do it.

11:24.385 --> 11:26.353
[kushangaza]

11:27.488 --> 11:31.458
[tetemeko]

11:42.136 --> 11:48.876
[akiimba huko Harkonnen]

11:53.414 --> 11:54.949
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

11:57.552 --> 12:00.020
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

12:08.462 --> 12:11.065
[chanting inaendelea]

12:13.000 --> 12:15.769
Lor-- Lord Rabban.

12:15.803 --> 12:17.905
Now that the spice fields
have been secured,

12:17.938 --> 12:21.175
I strongly recommend bringing
all troops out
of Fremen territories.

12:21.208 --> 12:23.077
We're losing too many men
to the desert.

12:23.110 --> 12:24.411
[Rabban] Rats.

12:24.445 --> 12:26.080
[chanting continues
in the background]

12:26.113 --> 12:29.083
-I beg your pardon?
-We're losing men to rats.

12:30.451 --> 12:32.152
[akizungumza Harkonnen]

12:32.186 --> 12:34.321
Fremen!
I can't confirm, my Lord.

12:34.355 --> 12:36.190
Communications are hectic
in the open snas.

12:36.223 --> 12:39.093
Your orders were to control
sayari nzima.

12:41.095 --> 12:43.998
-We are.
-I see only half of it.

12:44.031 --> 12:45.232
[Harkonnen commnaer]
As you may recall,

12:45.266 --> 12:48.102
the South is uninhabitable,
my Lord.

12:50.437 --> 12:52.306
May I suggest
you get some rest?

12:52.339 --> 12:55.242
-[both grunt]
-Rats! Hairy rats!

12:55.276 --> 12:57.579
Kill them! Kill them!
Kill them all!

12:57.612 --> 12:59.547
Kill them all!

12:59.581 --> 13:02.116
<i>Rats!</i> [echoes]

13:02.149 --> 13:05.085
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

13:16.430 --> 13:18.332
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

13:29.109 --> 13:31.078
[Stilgar communicates
gutturally]

13:36.283 --> 13:38.118
[Fremen sentinel communicates
gutturally]

13:45.993 --> 13:47.161
[sentinel leader
speaks Chakobsa]

13:47.194 --> 13:48.329
[anaongea Chakobsa]

13:48.362 --> 13:49.597
He's asking why we're so late.

13:49.631 --> 13:51.432
[continues conversing
huko Chakobsa]

13:55.436 --> 13:56.504
He thinks you're spies.

13:56.538 --> 13:59.206
[akizungumza kwa Chakobsa]

13:59.239 --> 14:01.543
-[Chani] He said--
-I got that.

14:01.576 --> 14:05.112
-Thanks.
-[Stilgar] Stay close to me.
Hmm?

14:05.145 --> 14:06.146
[anaongea Chakobsa]

14:06.180 --> 14:08.215
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

14:14.455 --> 14:15.590
[kuzungumza bila kujulikana]

14:25.299 --> 14:26.367
Sietch Tabr.

14:38.379 --> 14:40.914
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

14:49.423 --> 14:50.357
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

14:56.263 --> 14:59.133
-[angry, indistinct shouting
huko Chakobsa]
[Stilgar anaongea Chakobsa]

15:14.281 --> 15:19.353
[woman vocalizing]

15:19.386 --> 15:22.557
[akizungumza kwa Chakobsa]

15:22.590 --> 15:26.059
[all wakipiga kelele huko Chakobsa]

15:40.642 --> 15:43.310
[angry, indistinct shouting]

15:43.343 --> 15:45.312
[man akizungumza Chakobsa]

15:58.626 --> 16:00.427
[angry shouting inaendelea]

16:00.461 --> 16:01.663
[man] <i>Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

16:04.097 --> 16:08.636
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

16:08.670 --> 16:11.472
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

16:11.506 --> 16:13.373
[elders muttering]

16:16.376 --> 16:17.645
[all laughing]

16:26.153 --> 16:28.422
[all laughing]

16:51.679 --> 16:53.280
[oldest elder sighs]

16:53.313 --> 16:55.583
[oldest elder groans,
speaks Chakobsa]

16:57.652 --> 16:59.721
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

17:01.589 --> 17:04.191
Look how your Bene Gesserit
propagnaa has taken root.

17:07.227 --> 17:09.162
Some yam already think
I'm their messiah.

17:11.098 --> 17:12.165
Others...

17:13.734 --> 17:14.702
false prophet.

17:16.369 --> 17:19.373
I must sway the non-believers.

17:19.406 --> 17:22.409
If they follow me,
we can disrupt
spice production.

17:22.442 --> 17:24.278
That's the only way
I can get to the Emperor.

17:25.880 --> 17:27.481
Baba yako didn't believe
in revenge.

17:28.650 --> 17:29.584
[Paulo] Yeah, well, I do.

17:36.323 --> 17:38.425
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

17:49.369 --> 17:52.172
[indistinct whispering]

18:03.283 --> 18:04.217
[Jessica] What is happening?

18:05.853 --> 18:07.287
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

18:07.321 --> 18:09.456
[Fremen akicheka]

18:10.592 --> 18:11.458
[anapumua]

18:13.293 --> 18:14.562
What is it?

18:14.596 --> 18:16.296
[Paulo] There is spice
in the food.

18:16.330 --> 18:17.632
[woman speaks Chakobsa]

18:17.665 --> 18:18.733
[Fremen akicheka]

18:18.766 --> 18:19.667
[Chani akizungumza Chakobsa]

18:26.774 --> 18:28.241
-[anadhihaki]
-[Stilgar] Woman.

18:30.277 --> 18:32.179
Come with me.

18:32.212 --> 18:35.449
[praying watermasters
chant huko Chakobsa]

18:35.482 --> 18:39.152
[male watermaster
speaks Chakobsa]

18:39.186 --> 18:43.156
[praying watermasters
chant huko Chakobsa]

18:43.190 --> 18:46.193
[chanting inaendelea]

19:38.846 --> 19:39.747
[exhales deeply]

19:41.783 --> 19:45.252
[Stilgar] Thirty-eight million
decaliters.

19:45.285 --> 19:50.792
None of us,
even dying of thirst,
would ever drink this water.

19:50.825 --> 19:51.859
This is...

19:53.393 --> 19:54.529
sacred.

19:58.666 --> 19:59.767
Jamis' water.

20:01.435 --> 20:04.639
We have a thousna such places.

20:05.740 --> 20:09.010
When we have enough water,

20:09.043 --> 20:13.648
the <i>Lisan al-Gaib</i> will change
the face of Arrakis.

20:13.681 --> 20:16.316
He will bring back the trees.
He will bring back...

20:18.318 --> 20:19.520
a Green Paradise.

20:22.657 --> 20:24.357
[minong'ono] So many souls.

20:24.391 --> 20:28.328
[bell rings]

20:28.361 --> 20:29.997
[anaongea Chakobsa]

20:30.031 --> 20:30.998
[Stilgar grunts]

20:34.702 --> 20:38.438
Never give your water away,
not even for the dead. Hmm?

20:41.341 --> 20:42.744
Why are you showing me this?

20:42.777 --> 20:44.478
Because you are Bene Gesserit.

20:44.512 --> 20:48.448
Because you understna
the prophecies.

20:48.482 --> 20:51.786
The mother of
the <i>Lisan al-Gaib</i>
will be a Mama Mchungaji.

20:53.054 --> 20:55.590
Our Reverend Mother is dying.

20:57.424 --> 20:59.627
[minong'ono]
You want me to take her place?

20:59.660 --> 21:02.530
Yes, I do.

21:04.999 --> 21:06.433
You believe in Paulo?

21:09.103 --> 21:10.638
There are signs.

21:11.973 --> 21:13.775
Ndiyo.

21:13.808 --> 21:15.543
[chanting continues
in background]

21:15.576 --> 21:17.078
What if I would refuse?

21:17.111 --> 21:20.014
Mmm.
Then, he's not <i>Lisan al-Gaib,</i>

21:20.047 --> 21:22.083
na you have no purpose
to serve.

21:22.116 --> 21:26.087
What else is left to do then
but to return your water
to the well?

21:26.120 --> 21:27.688
[bofya ulimi] Huh.

21:28.790 --> 21:31.358
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

21:31.391 --> 21:32.560
[Paulo] It's an honor, isn't it?

21:34.427 --> 21:35.830
I think you should
feel honored.

21:35.863 --> 21:37.899
Well, it was a choice
between this or death,

21:37.932 --> 21:39.767
so, you know, forgive me
if I'm not flattered.

21:41.936 --> 21:43.638
How does one become
a Reverend Mother?

21:43.671 --> 21:45.640
It's different from one culture
to another.

21:45.673 --> 21:47.575
Here on Arrakis,
I have no idea.

21:51.913 --> 21:54.081
You're afraid.

21:54.115 --> 21:56.017
Reverend Mothers are tasked
with holding the memories

21:56.050 --> 21:57.885
of all the Reverend Mothers
that came before them,

21:57.919 --> 22:01.088
so I'll be given centuries
of pain na sorrow.

22:01.923 --> 22:02.790
Is it dangerous?

22:03.791 --> 22:05.425
It's lethal for men.

22:06.060 --> 22:07.862
That's for sure.

22:07.895 --> 22:11.398
[Stilgar anaongea Chakobsa]

22:11.431 --> 22:12.533
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

22:12.567 --> 22:14.802
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

22:27.181 --> 22:29.349
[suspenseful music
continues playing]

22:30.585 --> 22:31.451
[Jessica gasps softly]

22:40.595 --> 22:44.632
[indistinct whispering,
chanting]

22:58.145 --> 22:59.547
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

23:01.015 --> 23:04.986
[group laughing]

23:16.197 --> 23:18.132
What are you guys
laughing kuhusu?

23:18.165 --> 23:19.399
Don't bother. [anacheka]

23:24.572 --> 23:25.773
You don't believe in all this?

23:25.806 --> 23:27.440
[Chani] No, we don't.

23:27.474 --> 23:29.143
[Shishakli]
These are old Southern beliefs.

23:29.176 --> 23:31.444
Southern beliefs?

23:31.478 --> 23:34.782
Southern tribes believe
a messiah will come
to deliver us from evil.

23:34.815 --> 23:36.884
You don't believe
in the <i>Lisan al-Gaib?</i>

23:36.918 --> 23:39.220
[Chani] We believe in Fremen.

23:39.253 --> 23:41.589
[group akizungumza Chakobsa]

23:41.622 --> 23:44.725
You want to control people,
you tell them
a messiah will come.

23:44.759 --> 23:48.495
-Mm-hmm.
-Then they'll wait
for centuries.

23:48.529 --> 23:50.031
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

23:51.565 --> 23:54.635
Now, we must pray.

24:02.109 --> 24:03.077
What kuhusu him?

24:03.110 --> 24:04.812
-[Chani] Stilgar?
-Mm-hmm.

24:04.845 --> 24:07.949
He's from the South.
You didn't notice his accent?

24:07.982 --> 24:10.685
[Chani na Shishakli laugh]

24:10.718 --> 24:12.820
[Stilgar praying huko Chakobsa]

24:13.988 --> 24:15.222
[anapumua]

24:17.091 --> 24:18.259
What'll happen to my mother?

24:18.292 --> 24:19.660
[akizungumza kwa Chakobsa]

24:19.694 --> 24:20.828
[group laughs]

24:20.861 --> 24:21.896
[Chani akizungumza katika Chakobsa]

24:26.167 --> 24:27.768
[group laughs]

24:27.802 --> 24:31.706
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

24:36.043 --> 24:38.112
[Fremen nuns
akizungumza katika Chakobsa]

24:40.715 --> 24:43.551
[minong'ono] I must not fear.
Fear is the mind-killer.

24:43.584 --> 24:46.554
Fear, the little death
that brings total obliteration.

24:46.587 --> 24:48.656
I will face my fear. I will...

24:48.689 --> 24:51.659
[Fremen nuns continue
akizungumza katika Chakobsa]

24:53.627 --> 24:56.864
[old watermaster
akizungumza Chakobsa]

25:13.714 --> 25:14.615
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

25:15.282 --> 25:16.183
What is it?

25:16.217 --> 25:17.151
[distorted voice] Drink!

25:23.257 --> 25:28.095
[anapumua sana]

25:28.129 --> 25:29.663
[indistinct whispering]

25:29.697 --> 25:30.664
[kuguna]

25:36.804 --> 25:37.671
[kushtuka]

25:40.374 --> 25:43.644
[kusonga]

25:43.677 --> 25:45.980
[pained grunts]

25:54.188 --> 25:55.056
[kushtuka]

25:56.190 --> 25:58.125
[shuddering breaths]

26:17.878 --> 26:19.680
[pained grunts]

26:32.326 --> 26:33.360
[kushtuka]

26:35.663 --> 26:36.964
[kushtuka]

26:38.732 --> 26:40.101
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

26:43.804 --> 26:44.672
[kushtuka]

26:45.406 --> 26:46.841
[kutetemeka]

26:50.344 --> 26:52.947
[angry, indistinct shouting]

26:52.980 --> 26:56.083
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

27:00.988 --> 27:01.989
[anaugulia]

27:02.022 --> 27:03.190
[angry, indistinct shouting]

27:03.224 --> 27:05.359
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

27:10.431 --> 27:12.833
[angry, indistinct shouting]

27:22.076 --> 27:24.245
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

27:25.446 --> 27:27.882
[Chani akizungumza Chakobsa]

27:27.915 --> 27:30.217
She's right. She's right!

27:32.386 --> 27:33.420
It's no miracle.

27:35.022 --> 27:37.892
My mother was trained
to do that.

27:37.925 --> 27:40.828
Poison transmutation
is something advanced
Bene Gesserit can do.

27:44.298 --> 27:45.432
I'm not the <i>Mahdi.</i>

27:49.103 --> 27:50.304
I'm not here to lead.

27:56.511 --> 27:59.747
Let me fight beside you.
That's all I'm asking.

28:05.319 --> 28:06.887
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

28:16.797 --> 28:18.866
[Fremen akizungumza Chakobsa]

28:23.204 --> 28:24.138
[Paulo] How are you?

28:25.172 --> 28:26.173
[Jessica] Better.

28:27.274 --> 28:28.275
[Paulo] How is she?

28:29.910 --> 28:31.412
[Jessica] She was frightened,
but she's...

28:33.080 --> 28:34.081
she's okay.

28:36.317 --> 28:38.352
[Jessica breathes heavily]

28:40.287 --> 28:41.188
[Jessica whispers] Paulo.

28:44.425 --> 28:46.126
She talks to me.

28:49.330 --> 28:51.165
She believes in you.

28:51.198 --> 28:53.234
[ominous music playing]

28:54.569 --> 28:55.836
She says...

28:57.238 --> 29:01.075
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

29:03.210 --> 29:05.346
You're so close now.

29:05.379 --> 29:09.383
Only one step remains
na you will become
the <i>Kwisatz Haderach.</i>

29:10.484 --> 29:12.253
Only one step remains.

29:13.220 --> 29:14.855
You must do what I did.

29:14.888 --> 29:18.192
Lazima unywe
Maji ya Uzima.

29:18.225 --> 29:21.895
And your mind,
it's gon-- it's gonna open
na utaona.

29:22.896 --> 29:24.398
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

29:32.940 --> 29:37.579
[Stilgar] If you wanna fight
with us, first thing,
you must learn

29:37.612 --> 29:39.547
to be one with the desert.

29:41.181 --> 29:44.552
So, here is a tent
na enough food.

29:44.586 --> 29:49.323
I want you to cross
that small erg na come back.

29:50.124 --> 29:51.859
Travel by night.

29:51.892 --> 29:53.360
You know how to use
a paracompass?

29:53.394 --> 29:54.361
-Ndiyo.
-Oh.

29:56.130 --> 29:57.498
[Stilgar sighs]

29:57.532 --> 29:59.066
Anything else I should know?

29:59.099 --> 30:01.503
Uh, beside the worms
na the Harkonnens,

30:01.536 --> 30:05.272
beware ya trapdoor spiders.

30:05.306 --> 30:08.876
Centipedes are very nasty.
Not the big ones.

30:08.909 --> 30:10.545
They are harmless.

30:10.578 --> 30:14.248
But the little ones,
you have to worry kuhusu.
And... Oh!

30:16.950 --> 30:20.387
Don't ever,
ever listen to the jinn.

30:22.657 --> 30:24.325
-The jinn?
-Jinn.

30:24.358 --> 30:26.026
Desert spirits.

30:27.461 --> 30:30.130
They whisper at night.

30:30.164 --> 30:34.268
[imitates Jinn whispering]

30:34.301 --> 30:37.104
They, they can possess you.

30:37.137 --> 30:41.175
Really, be careful.
They are demons.

30:42.242 --> 30:44.311
[growls, laughs]

30:44.345 --> 30:46.213
But it's true.
Don't listen to them.

30:47.281 --> 30:48.215
[Stilgar grunts]

30:50.084 --> 30:51.318
[Chani akizungumza Chakobsa]

30:57.257 --> 30:58.325
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

31:04.231 --> 31:06.333
[Fremen akizungumza Chakobsa]

32:03.257 --> 32:04.958
[Jamis laughs, echoes]

32:05.560 --> 32:07.027
[Paulo panting]

32:11.633 --> 32:13.167
[Paulo] Jamis.

32:15.570 --> 32:18.005
[Chani] You snawalk
like a drunk lizard.

32:18.573 --> 32:19.373
[anacheka]

32:21.241 --> 32:22.744
Yeah, I'm doing
pretty good so far.

32:22.777 --> 32:25.345
Yeah, well, you're not even
in worm territory yet.

32:44.364 --> 32:46.066
[Chani] You have to break up
your rhythm.

32:50.170 --> 32:52.406
Like this.

32:52.439 --> 32:55.309
[Paulo] Now, that's interesting
because in the filmbooks
I've studied,

32:55.342 --> 32:58.613
the anthropologists say,
in order to properly snawalk,
you actually have--

33:02.416 --> 33:04.552
Never mind. Please keep going.

33:13.193 --> 33:15.162
[soft music playing]

33:33.080 --> 33:36.416
You know, I'm the only one
who believes you're gonna
make it until summer?

33:36.450 --> 33:38.218
Everyone else thinks
you won't make it two weeks.

33:39.587 --> 33:41.054
If you wanna follow us
in the desert,

33:41.088 --> 33:42.524
you need to know
how windtraps work.

33:42.557 --> 33:44.358
So, listen to me.

33:44.391 --> 33:46.661
They're simple,
but they require
constant attention.

33:46.694 --> 33:50.163
Uh, this right here,
it captures the moisture

33:50.197 --> 33:51.633
na then it carries it
into that pocket.

33:52.734 --> 33:55.803
Uh, na these are the filters.

33:55.837 --> 33:57.505
They need to be changed
every three days.

33:59.406 --> 34:00.274
Je!

34:02.744 --> 34:03.745
[anacheka]

34:05.112 --> 34:06.614
Stop looking at me like that.

34:12.152 --> 34:13.688
[Jessica]
He's training with the Fremen.

34:13.721 --> 34:15.690
He will be back soon.
Don't worry.

34:16.824 --> 34:17.692
Mm-hmm.

34:19.259 --> 34:22.730
You're right. If we want
to protect your brother,

34:22.764 --> 34:25.867
we need all the Fremen
to believe in the prophecy.

34:25.900 --> 34:27.668
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

34:30.437 --> 34:34.708
<i>We must convert</i>
<i>the non-believers one by one.</i>

34:36.844 --> 34:39.379
<i>We need to start</i>
<i>with the weaker ones.</i>

34:40.547 --> 34:42.282
<i>The vulnerable ones.</i>

34:43.851 --> 34:46.386
<i>The ones who fear us.</i>

34:52.292 --> 34:55.329
[Fedaykin fighter
breathes heavily]

35:09.476 --> 35:11.879
[Fedaykin fighter whispers]
Hey, get out of here. Go.

35:28.195 --> 35:31.365
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

36:19.246 --> 36:21.248
[Fedaykin fighter
kupumua sana]

36:32.894 --> 36:34.662
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

36:34.696 --> 36:36.531
[blade swishing]

36:36.564 --> 36:39.232
[Askari wa Harkonnen
na Fedaykin fighters grunt]

36:47.608 --> 36:49.844
[grunting inaendelea]

36:54.582 --> 36:56.316
-[Paulo] You okay?
-[Chani] Yeah.

36:58.452 --> 36:59.620
[akizungumza Harkonnen]

36:59.654 --> 37:02.523
[rapid gunfire]

37:02.557 --> 37:03.691
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

37:03.725 --> 37:05.626
[rapid gunfire]

37:09.530 --> 37:10.865
[Fedaykin fighter grunts]

37:12.900 --> 37:16.537
[Chani na Paulo grunt, pant]

37:30.685 --> 37:31.953
[Fedaykin fighter na Chani
wakipiga kelele huko Chakobsa]

37:33.755 --> 37:34.889
[Chani] Let's go! Move!

37:34.922 --> 37:36.023
[both grunt]

37:46.067 --> 37:48.468
[Paulo na Harkonnen soldier
grunt]

37:52.439 --> 37:53.674
[Chani] Load.

38:01.682 --> 38:03.316
[Paulo anaguna]

38:03.350 --> 38:04.719
[blade clanking]

38:05.953 --> 38:07.054
[Askari wa Harkonnen shouts]

38:09.857 --> 38:11.358
[Paulo anaguna]

38:13.694 --> 38:14.896
[Paulo] Chani!

38:19.934 --> 38:20.802
[Chani] Reload!

38:35.583 --> 38:37.084
[Chani] Ugh! Reload.

38:37.118 --> 38:38.385
[Paulo] Oh, watch out!

38:38.418 --> 38:39.854
[both grunt, pant]

38:47.829 --> 38:49.697
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

38:54.936 --> 38:57.104
[Paulo] Its shield will
only open when it fires.

38:57.138 --> 38:58.806
[Chani] I know that.
What do you think
I'm trying to do?

38:58.840 --> 39:01.843
[Paulo] I'll trigger it.
On my signal. Be ready.

39:24.632 --> 39:25.933
[Paulo] Go!

39:27.702 --> 39:29.604
[kuguna] Ah, shit!

39:29.637 --> 39:30.671
[Paulo panting]

39:32.073 --> 39:33.941
-Go! Go!
-[rapid gunfire]

39:33.975 --> 39:35.776
[grunts, anaugulia]

39:41.048 --> 39:42.683
[Askari wa Harkonnen screams]

39:42.717 --> 39:44.986
[explodes]

39:45.019 --> 39:47.420
[Chani laughs]

39:47.454 --> 39:49.456
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

40:02.169 --> 40:03.638
[Chani na Paulo grunt]

40:07.775 --> 40:09.043
[Wapiganaji wa Fedaykin cheering]

40:12.479 --> 40:13.480
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

40:14.481 --> 40:16.183
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

40:30.164 --> 40:31.666
[Shishakli sniffing]

40:31.699 --> 40:33.534
[akizungumza kwa Chakobsa]

40:33.567 --> 40:35.569
[all laughing]

40:39.974 --> 40:41.809
Who taught you
to fight like that?

40:41.842 --> 40:43.611
-My old masters.
-Hmm.

40:43.644 --> 40:44.912
They were close friends.

40:48.015 --> 40:51.152
They were massacred.
Alongside my father.

40:56.724 --> 40:59.894
You've been fighting
the Harkonnens for decades.

40:59.927 --> 41:02.495
My family's been fighting them
for centuries.

41:02.530 --> 41:07.500
I know everything kuhusu them.
Their habits,
their ways of thinking.

41:07.535 --> 41:08.769
You know everything
kuhusu the desert.

41:08.803 --> 41:12.506
You harness
the very power of it.

41:12.540 --> 41:17.278
We can stop them together,
bury them in the sna
where they belong.

41:17.311 --> 41:19.780
So that this planet
can be yours once more.

41:19.814 --> 41:23.584
[deeply inhales] What would you
have us do? Huh?

41:23.617 --> 41:25.519
What would you do, Stilgar?

41:25.553 --> 41:29.623
I? I would... [anapumua]
would strike
even further north.

41:29.657 --> 41:31.525
Then I will go further north.

41:31.559 --> 41:34.228
And the further north you go,
the more likely it is you die.

41:34.261 --> 41:35.896
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

41:45.906 --> 41:47.541
[Wapiganaji wa Fedaykin chattering]

41:51.245 --> 41:52.947
[all agreeing]

41:52.980 --> 41:54.782
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

41:58.119 --> 42:01.222
[Stilgar]
I see strength in you.

42:01.255 --> 42:02.623
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

42:02.656 --> 42:03.524
[all agreeing]

42:06.861 --> 42:08.095
Come, come.

42:08.129 --> 42:09.730
[man laughing]

42:18.205 --> 42:23.911
You shall be know
among us as <i>Usul.</i>

42:23.944 --> 42:25.679
-[man] <i>Usul.</i>
<i>-Usul.</i>

42:25.713 --> 42:29.784
[Stilgar] <i>Usul.</i> And now,
a Fedaykin is a fighter

42:29.817 --> 42:31.018
na needs a war name.

42:31.986 --> 42:33.287
You must choose.

42:38.159 --> 42:39.627
How do you call the, uh...

42:41.062 --> 42:42.797
The small desert mouse, again?

42:42.830 --> 42:44.198
[all laughing]

42:44.231 --> 42:45.933
<i>-Muad'Dib?</i>
-[Paulo] <i>Muad'Dib.</i>

42:45.966 --> 42:48.602
No, no, no. [shusha]

42:48.636 --> 42:52.306
<i>Muad'Dib</i> is wise
in the ways ya desert.

42:52.339 --> 42:53.741
<i>Muad'Dib...</i>

42:54.775 --> 42:57.211
[anapumua] creates his own water.

42:57.244 --> 43:01.115
The constellation that points
to the North Star,
we call <i>Muad'Dib.</i>

43:01.148 --> 43:02.950
"The One Who Points the Way."

43:04.819 --> 43:06.053
That is a powerful name.

43:10.991 --> 43:15.062
Now you are our brother. Mmm.

43:15.096 --> 43:18.232
Paulo <i>Muad'Dib Usul.</i>

43:20.167 --> 43:22.803
[all cheering]

43:24.772 --> 43:25.873
[man 1] <i>Muad'Dib Usul.</i>

43:26.707 --> 43:27.775
<i>Muad'Dib Usul.</i>

43:29.777 --> 43:31.045
<i>Muad'Dib Usul.</i>

43:31.078 --> 43:33.314
[Paulo na Stilgar laugh]

43:33.347 --> 43:35.850
<i>Muad'Dib Usul.</i> Mm.

43:36.784 --> 43:37.685
[man] <i>Muad'Dib.</i>

43:40.921 --> 43:41.856
[minong'ono] <i>Usul.</i>

43:59.440 --> 44:02.042
[kupiga kelele] Hey! Stilgar!

44:02.076 --> 44:04.678
[Stilgar speaks Chakobsa,
laughs]

44:16.924 --> 44:18.325
Father, I found my way.

44:18.359 --> 44:20.694
[soft music playing]

44:26.400 --> 44:29.403
[footsteps approaching]

44:35.510 --> 44:36.677
[Paulo] It's breathtaking.

44:38.445 --> 44:39.747
[anapumua]

44:45.419 --> 44:46.687
[Chani] Hmm.

44:48.255 --> 44:52.359
Look. Right there. Spice.

44:52.393 --> 44:55.229
Arrakis is so beautiful
when the sun is low.

45:02.903 --> 45:07.408
Where you're from, does water
really fall from the sky?

45:07.441 --> 45:09.743
Oh, hm, yes.

45:09.777 --> 45:12.947
Sometimes it rains
for weeks on Caladan.

45:12.980 --> 45:15.249
Where you see sna here,
imagine water.

45:18.419 --> 45:22.524
Our castle stnas on cliffs
high above the sea.

45:22.557 --> 45:25.492
If you dive in,
you can't reach the bottom.

45:25.527 --> 45:29.496
-[Chani] You dive in?
-Yes, it's called swimming.

45:29.531 --> 45:32.333
[laughs] I don't--
I don't believe you, <i>Usul.</i>

45:32.366 --> 45:33.434
<i>Usul.</i>

45:36.136 --> 45:37.371
What's your secret name?

45:39.807 --> 45:41.442
<i>Sihaya.</i>

45:41.475 --> 45:42.843
<i>-Sihaya.</i>
-Hmm.

45:44.311 --> 45:46.046
What does that mean?

45:46.080 --> 45:47.915
Means Desert Spring.

45:47.948 --> 45:49.016
"Desert Spring."

45:50.951 --> 45:52.419
-I love it.
-I hate it.

45:53.588 --> 45:55.456
It's from some stupid prophecy.

45:56.490 --> 45:57.525
I prefer Chani.

45:58.593 --> 46:00.127
I prefer Chani, too, then.

46:07.234 --> 46:09.169
Do you think Stilgar
would teach me?

46:09.203 --> 46:10.904
-[Chani] To ride?
-[Paulo] Yeah.

46:10.938 --> 46:14.174
[Chani laughs]
No. Only Fremen ride worms.

46:14.208 --> 46:15.976
Well, I thought I'd become one,
didn't I?

46:16.010 --> 46:17.878
By name, not by blood.

46:20.214 --> 46:24.918
Your blood comes
from Dukes na Great Houses.

46:26.954 --> 46:29.256
We don't have that here.

46:29.290 --> 46:33.294
Here, we're equal,
men na women alike.

46:33.327 --> 46:35.496
What we do,
we do for the benefit of all.

46:35.530 --> 46:37.898
Well, I'd very much like
to be equal to you.

46:44.138 --> 46:47.374
Paulo <i>Muad'Dib Usul...</i>

46:49.276 --> 46:51.445
maybe you could be Fremen.

46:54.649 --> 46:56.050
Maybe I'll show you the way.

47:34.054 --> 47:36.090
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

47:41.195 --> 47:43.997
[milio ya bunduki]
-[explodes]

47:52.940 --> 47:54.576
[all akizungumza Chakobsa]

48:17.264 --> 48:21.636
[women screaming]

48:21.669 --> 48:22.537
[bang]

48:25.105 --> 48:26.407
[Baron Harkonnen] Rabban.

48:26.440 --> 48:28.075
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

48:34.549 --> 48:37.251
[anapumua sana]

48:37.284 --> 48:41.656
[Baron Harkonnen]
Fremen attacks on your watch.

48:41.689 --> 48:47.662
Your orders were to restore
spice production
to full capacity.

48:47.695 --> 48:50.130
Do you know
what it means if you fail?

48:51.733 --> 48:55.637
The Emperor will take spice
out of our control.

48:56.638 --> 48:58.272
Tighten your grip, Rabban.

48:58.305 --> 49:00.340
[breathes heavily, whispers]
Uncle.

49:00.374 --> 49:02.677
[Baron Harkonnen]
Or feel mine on your neck.

49:12.319 --> 49:16.423
[breathes heavily, anaugulia]

49:18.392 --> 49:20.528
-[Chani] <i>Usul? Usul.</i>
-[Paulo gasps]

49:20.562 --> 49:23.363
It's okay. It's okay.

49:26.668 --> 49:27.535
Hey.

49:30.471 --> 49:33.575
I'm here, I'm here.

49:33.608 --> 49:36.678
It's been a while
since you've had
one of those nightmares.

49:36.711 --> 49:37.679
Mm.

49:41.549 --> 49:43.685
[Chani] Tell me,
what was it kuhusu?

49:47.154 --> 49:49.724
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

49:49.757 --> 49:53.060
[Paulo] <i>Nothing's clear.</i>
<i>It's only fragments.</i>

49:53.093 --> 49:55.062
[water drips]

49:55.095 --> 49:59.032
<i>I'm in the South,</i>
<i>na I'm following someone.</i>

50:00.400 --> 50:02.336
<i>And it triggers a holy war.</i>

50:05.807 --> 50:09.511
<i>Millions na millions of people</i>
<i>starving to death...</i>

50:10.845 --> 50:12.212
<i>because of me.</i>

50:18.118 --> 50:21.255
[Chani] You've been exposed
to spice for a long time.

50:21.288 --> 50:23.357
It can create weird dreams.

50:23.390 --> 50:25.025
[anapumua sana]

50:30.397 --> 50:31.265
It's a big day.

50:33.433 --> 50:35.068
We can ask Stilgar
to call it off.

50:35.102 --> 50:37.572
No. I'm fine.

50:39.741 --> 50:41.375
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

50:53.621 --> 50:54.556
[Stilgar] <i>Usul.</i>

50:57.391 --> 50:59.326
I tuned it myself.

51:01.461 --> 51:02.697
-Here.
-[Paulo] Thanks.

51:03.531 --> 51:05.465
[anapumua]

51:05.499 --> 51:09.336
Don't try to impress anyone.
You are brave.
We all know that.

51:10.304 --> 51:12.674
Heh? Be simple.

51:12.707 --> 51:16.109
Be direct. Nothing fancy.

51:16.143 --> 51:18.278
-Nothing fancy.
-Hey, I'm serious.

51:18.312 --> 51:20.782
Nothing fancy or you will shame
my teaching.

51:20.815 --> 51:24.852
I won't shame you.
I understna.

51:24.886 --> 51:29.524
<i>Shai-Hulud</i> decides today
if you become Fremen,
or if you die.

51:30.223 --> 51:31.593
[anacheka]

51:31.626 --> 51:32.760
[Stilgar anaongea Chakobsa]

51:37.565 --> 51:38.666
Hey, <i>Muad'Dib!</i>

51:38.700 --> 51:41.736
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

51:41.769 --> 51:44.739
[all laughing]

51:50.477 --> 51:51.579
[Stilgar sighs]

51:53.514 --> 51:55.449
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

51:59.687 --> 52:00.555
[anapumua]

52:02.757 --> 52:06.226
[Paulo panting]

52:12.366 --> 52:13.233
[kuguna]

52:20.508 --> 52:21.509
[minong'ono] Lower.

52:23.443 --> 52:25.913
[kuhema]

52:40.595 --> 52:41.461
[kuguna]

52:43.230 --> 52:44.832
[kuhema]

52:45.833 --> 52:48.235
Okay. Okay.

52:56.443 --> 52:58.713
[whirrs]

52:58.746 --> 53:01.783
[kupiga]
[Paul akihema]

53:15.830 --> 53:18.566
[exhales]

53:19.934 --> 53:21.836
[kuhema]

53:38.820 --> 53:40.922
[vibrating]

53:43.624 --> 53:44.592
[ anashusha pumzi polepole]

53:47.327 --> 53:49.262
[all murmuring]

53:49.296 --> 53:51.866
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

53:59.907 --> 54:04.444
Okay. Okay. Okay.

54:09.316 --> 54:10.985
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

54:13.955 --> 54:15.690
[Paulo panting]

54:41.949 --> 54:43.918
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

54:52.026 --> 54:53.060
[Paulo] Okay.

55:10.678 --> 55:12.013
Okay. Okay!

55:12.046 --> 55:13.581
[kupiga kelele]

55:19.787 --> 55:20.721
[kuguna]

55:24.091 --> 55:25.059
[kuguna]

55:34.135 --> 55:35.069
[kupiga kelele]

55:36.904 --> 55:37.939
Come on!

55:48.883 --> 55:49.784
Whoa!

56:41.235 --> 56:43.470
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

56:49.911 --> 56:51.512
[Fremen cheering huko Chakobsa]

56:51.545 --> 56:53.180
[anacheka]

56:53.214 --> 56:54.515
You're a rider!

56:55.516 --> 56:57.118
[kupiga kelele]

56:57.151 --> 56:59.520
[Fremen cheering]

57:10.765 --> 57:12.066
[Paulo panting]

57:16.103 --> 57:17.705
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

57:22.977 --> 57:27.815
[all wakiimba huko Chakobsa]

57:57.812 --> 58:00.815
[nun wakipiga kelele huko Chakobsa]

58:07.822 --> 58:10.558
[all akizungumza katika Chakobsa]

58:10.591 --> 58:12.760
[nun akizungumza katika Chakobsa]

58:16.263 --> 58:17.865
[all akizungumza katika Chakobsa]

58:17.898 --> 58:19.934
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

58:21.602 --> 58:23.838
[all akizungumza katika Chakobsa]

58:30.211 --> 58:31.879
[all akizungumza katika Chakobsa]

58:38.853 --> 58:40.855
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

58:42.690 --> 58:44.258
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

58:50.064 --> 58:52.600
[Jessica] Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.
I know they do.

58:55.336 --> 58:58.005
<i>Our task in the North</i>
<i>is nearly done.</i>

58:58.039 --> 58:59.774
<i>They believe in Paulo.</i>

59:00.808 --> 59:03.044
<i>Now we go South.</i>

59:03.077 --> 59:06.747
<i>There are millions</i>
<i>of fundamentalists there.</i>

59:06.781 --> 59:09.116
<i>They will protect him</i>
<i>when he comes.</i>

59:11.786 --> 59:15.956
<i>The</i> Kwisatz Haderach
<i>will be born in the South.</i>

59:19.160 --> 59:20.728
[both kupumua sana]

59:24.265 --> 59:26.067
[kunong'ona kwa Chakobsa]

59:29.970 --> 59:31.739
As long as I breathe.

59:36.177 --> 59:37.144
What's wrong?

59:43.217 --> 59:44.185
Chani.

59:44.218 --> 59:45.786
There will be trouble.

59:47.955 --> 59:49.223
What are you talking kuhusu?

59:53.060 --> 59:54.662
Chani, what do you mean?

59:54.695 --> 59:56.030
The way they look at you.

59:57.398 --> 59:58.866
They worship you now.

01:00:01.769 --> 01:00:04.238
Fedaykin,
wanahesabu ushindi wako.

01:00:04.271 --> 01:00:06.874
Wanasema wewe
unaweza kuona siku zijazo.

01:00:06.907 --> 01:00:08.676
Kunong'ona," <i>Lisan al-Gaib."</i>

01:00:09.944 --> 01:00:11.278
Mimi si masihi.

01:00:14.048 --> 01:00:17.218
Mimi ni Fedaykin wa Sietch Tabr.

01:00:17.251 --> 01:00:19.954
Walakini, tunayo Bene Gesserit
kati yetu,

01:00:19.987 --> 01:00:21.322
kuwasha moto
ya hadithi yako,

01:00:21.355 --> 01:00:22.890
wakisema wewe ni Mmoja.

01:00:30.264 --> 01:00:31.832
[Paulo anapumua]

01:00:36.170 --> 01:00:39.707
[kupiga]
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

01:00:44.345 --> 01:00:45.880
[Jessica] Mm.

01:00:45.913 --> 01:00:47.047
[mpiganaji wa kiume wa Fedaykin
akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:00:50.317 --> 01:00:52.153
Anasema unapaswa
kuja pamoja nasi.

01:00:53.020 --> 01:00:54.088
Unajua siwezi.

01:00:54.989 --> 01:00:56.423
Anauliza kwanini.

01:00:56.457 --> 01:00:58.425
Kwa sababu lazima niendelee
mapigano Kaskazini,

01:00:58.459 --> 01:01:00.661
ili kukulinda chini
huko Kusini.

01:01:02.429 --> 01:01:06.066
Anasema anaweza kusema
unaposema uongo.

01:01:06.100 --> 01:01:09.403
Mwambie hiyo ni kwa sababu
mama yetu anaendelea kusambaa
hadithi hatari.

01:01:10.738 --> 01:01:11.839
[kupiga kelele kunaendelea]

01:01:17.011 --> 01:01:18.812
Anasema nini sasa?

01:01:18.846 --> 01:01:21.248
Anasema umepofushwa
kwa upendo,

01:01:21.282 --> 01:01:23.450
na anakukumbusha hivyo
lazima uhifadhi mkono wako

01:01:23.484 --> 01:01:25.319
kwa wengi
muungano wa kimkakati.

01:01:28.355 --> 01:01:31.325
Yeye pia anashangaa
kwanini huamini
katika wewe ni nani.

01:01:31.358 --> 01:01:32.726
Ninaamini.

01:01:32.760 --> 01:01:34.695
Naamini ninajali
kwa watu hawa.

01:01:36.297 --> 01:01:38.299
Na ninaamini ninatengeneza
tofauti katika vita hivi.

01:01:40.334 --> 01:01:42.069
Tumekaribia
kwenye malango ya mji.

01:01:42.102 --> 01:01:44.972
- Hiyo sio maana yake.
- Najua anamaanisha nini.

01:01:45.005 --> 01:01:47.341
Je, unafikiri mimi pia kujisikia
uzito wa unabii?

01:01:47.374 --> 01:01:49.343
Sio unabii.

01:01:49.376 --> 01:01:51.078
Ni hadithi ambayo wewe
endelea kusema,

01:01:51.111 --> 01:01:53.147
lakini sio hadithi yao,
ni yako.

01:01:53.180 --> 01:01:56.383
Wanastahili kuongozwa
na mmoja wao.

01:01:56.417 --> 01:01:59.119
Watu wako walifanya nini
kwa dunia hii inahuzunisha.

01:01:59.153 --> 01:02:00.821
Tuliwapa kitu
kutumaini.

01:02:00.854 --> 01:02:02.356
[kwa kelele] Hilo si tumaini!

01:02:07.494 --> 01:02:09.930
[mpiganaji wa kiume wa Fedaykin
akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:02:13.033 --> 01:02:13.901
[anadhihaki]

01:02:16.538 --> 01:02:18.038
Nitakuwa nakungoja.

01:02:19.473 --> 01:02:20.908
[sauti iliyopotoka] Sisi sote.

01:02:20.941 --> 01:02:22.910
[sauti za zamani zinasikika]
<i>Sisi sote.</i>

01:02:22.943 --> 01:02:24.278
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

01:03:04.285 --> 01:03:06.920
[Jessica]
Dhoruba hizo zinaonekana mbaya.

01:03:06.954 --> 01:03:08.789
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:03:35.049 --> 01:03:36.450
[Ndege anayeiga Stilgar]

01:03:42.222 --> 01:03:44.224
[mashine inazunguka]
[mlio wa kengele]

01:03:48.596 --> 01:03:50.497
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:03:54.001 --> 01:03:55.637
[Rabban] Kiasi gani?
[Askari wa Harkonnen]
Tumepoteza...

01:03:55.670 --> 01:03:58.339
asilimia themanini
ya mazao yetu ya mwisho.

01:03:58.372 --> 01:04:02.242
Mola wangu Rabban,
hupaswi kuondoka
mzunguko wa usalama.

01:04:02.276 --> 01:04:04.878
Mzunguko wa usalama?
Panya tayari wako ndani.

01:04:04.912 --> 01:04:06.548
Pepo wa Fremen
anaweza kuwa nao.

01:04:06.581 --> 01:04:08.282
[Rabban] Natumai hivyo.

01:04:08.315 --> 01:04:08.949
[Askari wa Harkonnen]
Tunawafuatilia, Bwana wangu.

01:04:10.150 --> 01:04:12.953
Leo, <i>Muad'Dib</i> kufa!

01:04:17.057 --> 01:04:19.126
[akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:04:51.959 --> 01:04:54.495
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza kupitia com]

01:04:54.529 --> 01:04:56.196
Yuko wapi?

01:04:56.230 --> 01:04:57.665
Bado hasi, Bwana wangu.

01:04:57.699 --> 01:04:59.266
[Rabban] Kwa nini ni lazima nifanye
kila kitu mwenyewe?

01:05:02.403 --> 01:05:03.470
Fungua safu!

01:05:03.505 --> 01:05:05.005
[Askari wa Harkonnen] safu wazi.

01:05:10.645 --> 01:05:12.946
[milio ya mashine]

01:05:12.980 --> 01:05:14.516
Maisha. Delta, delta, delta.

01:05:32.466 --> 01:05:34.536
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza kupitia com]

01:05:35.770 --> 01:05:37.037
Nimewapoteza.

01:05:40.775 --> 01:05:42.409
[kuguna]

01:05:42.443 --> 01:05:44.278
-Mgomo!
[Askari wa Harkonnen]
Naam, Bwana wangu.

01:06:07.401 --> 01:06:08.670
[mashine inasikika]

01:06:12.507 --> 01:06:15.142
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:06:30.190 --> 01:06:33.193
[Askari wa Harkonnen
kupumua sana]

01:06:47.474 --> 01:06:48.743
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:06:50.845 --> 01:06:53.681
[kupiga kelele] <i>Muad'Dib!</i>

01:06:53.715 --> 01:06:55.583
Jionyeshe! [mwangwi]

01:06:59.754 --> 01:07:04.057
[milio ya bunduki]
- Wanajeshi wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:07:08.262 --> 01:07:12.366
[miguno]
[mawimbi ya blade]

01:07:12.399 --> 01:07:15.803
[anapumua sana]
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:07:15.837 --> 01:07:18.372
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

01:07:18.405 --> 01:07:22.844
[vipande vya blade]
[bodies thud]

01:07:22.877 --> 01:07:26.413
[miguno]
[Askari wa Harkonnen
akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:07:26.446 --> 01:07:30.518
[Wapiganaji wa Fedaykin wakiimba]
<i>Muad'Dib! Muad'Dib! Muad'Dib!</i>

01:07:39.894 --> 01:07:42.329
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

01:07:43.463 --> 01:07:45.833
[wote wakilalamika]

01:08:01.616 --> 01:08:04.284
[Mpiganaji wa Fedaykin anapiga kelele]
[Rabban anaguna]

01:08:08.823 --> 01:08:10.090
[kuguna]

01:08:13.528 --> 01:08:16.731
[kuguna]

01:08:20.399 --> 01:08:21.536
[kupiga kelele]

01:08:21.569 --> 01:08:23.537
[miguno]
[Mpiganaji wa Fedaykin anapiga kelele]

01:08:23.571 --> 01:08:25.707
[Mpiganaji wa Fedaykin]
Kwa <i>Muad'Dib!</i> [kuguna]

01:08:25.740 --> 01:08:27.508
[kuhema]

01:08:38.352 --> 01:08:39.386
[Mfalme] <i>Muad'Dib.</i>

01:08:41.756 --> 01:08:45.760
Nabii mpya wa Fremen?

01:08:45.792 --> 01:08:48.696
[Binti Irulan]
Sio mara ya kwanza tunayo
alikuwa na msuguano na Fremen.

01:08:48.729 --> 01:08:50.531
Hakuna kati ya ukubwa huu.

01:08:54.736 --> 01:08:56.336
Kwa hivyo, binti yangu mpendwa ...

01:08:57.604 --> 01:08:59.807
ungeshughulika vipi
na nabii huyu?

01:09:01.341 --> 01:09:02.910
[anapumua sana]

01:09:06.212 --> 01:09:08.883
Kama hii <i>Muad'Dib</i>
ni mtu wa kidini,

01:09:10.618 --> 01:09:12.386
huwezi kutumia nguvu ya moja kwa moja.

01:09:13.888 --> 01:09:17.323
Ukandamizaji hufanya tu
dini inastawi.

01:09:17.357 --> 01:09:19.426
Utaishia tu
kujidhalilisha.

01:09:19.459 --> 01:09:21.194
Unadharau Sardakar yangu.

01:09:21.228 --> 01:09:23.898
Unadharau
nguvu ya imani.

01:09:25.667 --> 01:09:27.769
[anacheka]

01:09:27.801 --> 01:09:31.371
Utukufu wake unathibitisha
kwa mara nyingine tena kwamba alikuwa
mwanafunzi wangu mkali zaidi.

01:09:33.640 --> 01:09:36.511
-Ungependa kutuma wauaji?
[Princess Irulan] No.

01:09:36.544 --> 01:09:38.310
Manabii wanapata nguvu zaidi
wanapokufa.

01:09:39.981 --> 01:09:42.582
Acha migogoro
juu ya Arrakis kugeuka kuwa vita.

01:09:42.617 --> 01:09:45.787
Wewe basi kuleta amani.
Kama mwokozi.

01:09:48.321 --> 01:09:50.256
Ungekuwa mfalme wa kutisha.

01:09:52.560 --> 01:09:54.562
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

01:09:54.595 --> 01:09:57.532
<i>Muad'Dib.</i> Nabii.

01:09:57.565 --> 01:10:00.233
Yule anayeelekeza njia.

01:10:00.267 --> 01:10:02.436
Hizi ni zetu wenyewe
mifumo ya kidini,
sivyo?

01:10:02.469 --> 01:10:03.738
Hii ni kazi yetu.

01:10:07.407 --> 01:10:10.444
<i>Muad'Dib</i> maana yake kangaroo panya.

01:10:10.477 --> 01:10:12.379
Jina la vita isiyo ya kawaida
kwa Fremen.

01:10:14.582 --> 01:10:17.685
-Je kama Paul Atreides
walikuwa bado hai?
[imepotoshwa] Inatosha!

01:10:17.719 --> 01:10:21.856
Hii lazima isitoke.
Hata masikio ya baba yako.
Kuelewa?

01:10:22.790 --> 01:10:25.727
Ninaamini, Mama Mchungaji.

01:10:25.760 --> 01:10:28.996
[Mchungaji Mama Mohiam]
Ikiwa Paulo yu hai,
yaelekea anajua ukweli.

01:10:29.030 --> 01:10:30.965
Na lazima
Nyumba Kubwa kujifunza

01:10:30.998 --> 01:10:34.334
kwamba baba yako alikuwa nyuma
kufilisi
wa Atreides,

01:10:34.367 --> 01:10:37.705
baba yako atakabiliwa na vita
na kupoteza kiti cha enzi.

01:10:39.674 --> 01:10:41.008
Kisha kuna tumaini gani?

01:10:42.543 --> 01:10:43.410
Tumaini?

01:10:44.879 --> 01:10:49.016
Sisi ni Bene Gesserit.
Hatuna matumaini, tunapanga.

01:10:50.383 --> 01:10:54.354
Paulo sio tarajio letu pekee.

01:10:54.387 --> 01:10:59.392
Mpwa wa mwisho wa Baron,
Feyd-Rautha Harkonnen,
atarithi Arrakis.

01:11:00.928 --> 01:11:02.462
Anaweza kuwa jibu.

01:11:02.496 --> 01:11:05.032
Feyd-Rautha? Ana akili.

01:11:05.066 --> 01:11:07.001
Hilo halina umuhimu.

01:11:07.034 --> 01:11:11.371
Swali ni,
tunaweza kumdhibiti?

01:11:11.404 --> 01:11:12.807
Na ninakusudia kujua.

01:11:19.847 --> 01:11:21.549
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

01:11:29.924 --> 01:11:30.825
[anapumua]

01:11:36.130 --> 01:11:38.699
[Feyd-Rautha]
Je! ungependa nyama safi,
wapenzi wangu?

01:11:39.734 --> 01:11:42.870
-Mapafu? Au ini?
[miguno]

01:11:42.904 --> 01:11:45.973
[Feyd-Rautha]
Je, ungependa nini?
Nasikia ni kubwa leo.

01:11:46.007 --> 01:11:50.477
Vipuli vyako vipya
kwa siku hii maalum,

01:11:50.511 --> 01:11:53.346
na-Baron, Feyd-Rautha.

01:12:09.030 --> 01:12:10.765
[bwana silaha
kupumua sana]

01:12:12.399 --> 01:12:13.768
[mawimbi ya blade]
[mhudumu anasonga]

01:12:13.801 --> 01:12:15.402
[vikuku vya bakuli]

01:12:15.435 --> 01:12:17.437
[mhudumu anasonga]
[mapigo ya mwili]

01:12:17.470 --> 01:12:20.808
[visu vya blade]
[kupumua]

01:12:20.842 --> 01:12:22.677
[viboko]

01:12:22.710 --> 01:12:23.711
- [Feyd-Rautha] Kiwango cha juu
nje ya usawa.
[vinubi vinazomea]

01:12:23.744 --> 01:12:24.477
[Feyd-Rautha] Ni kidokezo.

01:12:25.546 --> 01:12:26.981
Inapaswa kuwa kali zaidi.

01:12:27.014 --> 01:12:28.716
[mtu akijitahidi, akigugumia]

01:12:33.154 --> 01:12:35.523
[kuhema]

01:12:37.725 --> 01:12:38.860
[mlango unafunguliwa]

01:12:41.195 --> 01:12:42.797
[bwana mtumwa] Njoo.

01:12:42.830 --> 01:12:44.866
[Lanville]
Sitakufa kama mjinga.

01:12:44.899 --> 01:12:46.033
Niue sasa.

01:12:46.067 --> 01:12:48.836
Hakuna dawa kwako leo,
Atreides.

01:12:51.138 --> 01:12:52.673
[umati ukishangilia]
[kupiga pembe]

01:12:52.707 --> 01:12:55.776
[mtangazaji wa uwanja wa gladiator
anaongea Harkonnen]

01:13:02.617 --> 01:13:04.451
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

01:13:11.025 --> 01:13:13.628
[kupiga mara kwa mara]

01:13:13.661 --> 01:13:15.663
[mtangazaji wa uwanja wa gladiator
inaendelea]

01:13:22.837 --> 01:13:25.039
[umati ukishangilia]

01:13:29.210 --> 01:13:32.412
[wote wakiimba huko Harkonnen]

01:13:52.767 --> 01:13:54.068
[kupiga mara kwa mara]

01:14:04.178 --> 01:14:06.213
[Lady Margot Fenring]
Karibu na Giedi Prime,
dada.

01:14:06.247 --> 01:14:08.516
Natumai safari zako
walikuwa wanakubalika.

01:14:08.549 --> 01:14:10.785
[Dada ya Bene Gesserit 1]
Njia ndefu kuja
tu kuangalia matarajio yetu

01:14:10.818 --> 01:14:12.753
kuhatarisha maisha yake, Lady Fenring.

01:14:12.787 --> 01:14:14.822
[Lady Margot Fenring] Hakuna hofu.

01:14:14.855 --> 01:14:16.557
Mapambano haya yote ni ya maonyesho.

01:14:18.025 --> 01:14:20.628
Lakini tutapata
kumtazama vizuri.

01:14:20.661 --> 01:14:24.198
[mtangazaji wa uwanja wa gladiator
akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:14:25.566 --> 01:14:27.601
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

01:14:33.240 --> 01:14:35.543
[kupuliza pembe]

01:14:42.683 --> 01:14:46.587
[umati wa watu wakiimba]
Feyd-Rautha! Feyd-Rautha!

01:15:15.116 --> 01:15:17.318
[umati ukishangilia]

01:15:17.351 --> 01:15:20.254
[mtangazaji wa uwanja wa gladiator
akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:16:00.961 --> 01:16:01.929
Huyo mtumwa hatumiwi dawa.

01:16:03.030 --> 01:16:04.765
Mdudu huyo anatembea moja kwa moja.

01:16:06.033 --> 01:16:07.268
Unapaswa kughairi pambano.

01:16:07.301 --> 01:16:10.137
Usiharibu
siku ya kuzaliwa ya mpwa wangu.

01:16:10.171 --> 01:16:12.740
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

01:16:12.773 --> 01:16:14.241
[anapumua sana]

01:16:16.911 --> 01:16:17.778
[kuguna]

01:16:25.820 --> 01:16:27.688
[kupiga kelele]

01:16:27.721 --> 01:16:28.722
[Feyd-Rautha anaguna]

01:16:31.258 --> 01:16:33.928
[wote wawili wanaguna, piga kelele]

01:16:36.931 --> 01:16:40.768
[wote wawili wanaguna, piga kelele]

01:16:43.137 --> 01:16:44.772
[kupiga kelele]

01:16:44.805 --> 01:16:46.974
[wote wawili wakiguna]

01:16:50.978 --> 01:16:51.879
[kupiga kelele]

01:16:54.048 --> 01:16:55.716
[kuhema]

01:16:57.751 --> 01:17:00.654
Heri ya kuzaliwa, mpwa mpendwa.

01:17:00.688 --> 01:17:02.790
[umati ukishangilia]

01:17:02.823 --> 01:17:05.359
[wote wawili wakiguna]

01:17:17.071 --> 01:17:19.039
[Dada ya Bene Gesserit 2]
Kwa nini hawaachi vita?

01:17:19.073 --> 01:17:20.941
Mipango ndani ya mipango.

01:17:20.975 --> 01:17:22.309
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

01:17:25.746 --> 01:17:27.148
Nionyeshe wewe ni nani.

01:17:33.888 --> 01:17:35.356
[umati ukishangilia]

01:17:44.131 --> 01:17:45.699
Huyo hapo.

01:17:46.400 --> 01:17:48.969
[pembe inavuma]

01:18:00.314 --> 01:18:02.416
[picadors wakilia]

01:18:12.793 --> 01:18:14.862
[wote wakipiga kelele, wakiguna]

01:18:15.829 --> 01:18:17.131
[kuhema]

01:18:19.099 --> 01:18:20.167
[Lanville anaguna]

01:18:20.201 --> 01:18:22.436
[wote wakipiga kelele, wakiguna]

01:18:28.008 --> 01:18:30.244
[Lanville anapiga kelele kwa uchungu,
anaugulia]

01:18:30.277 --> 01:18:32.079
Nyuma! Nyuma!

01:18:38.018 --> 01:18:40.387
[Lanville anaguna]
[Feyd-Rautha anacheka]

01:18:48.862 --> 01:18:49.897
[picadors wakilia]

01:18:49.930 --> 01:18:51.165
Kaa nyuma!

01:18:51.198 --> 01:18:53.500
[Lanville anaguna]

01:19:04.945 --> 01:19:07.181
[minong'ono] Umepigana
vizuri, Atreides.

01:19:08.282 --> 01:19:09.551
Hmm.

01:19:09.584 --> 01:19:11.185
[umati ukishangilia]
[Feyd-Rautha anaguna]

01:19:12.419 --> 01:19:14.288
[muziki wa kusisimua unacheza]

01:19:18.959 --> 01:19:23.297
[umati wa watu wakiimba]
Feyd-Rautha! Feyd-Rautha!

01:19:28.936 --> 01:19:30.304
Yeye ni ya kuvutia, kwa kweli.

01:19:30.337 --> 01:19:34.208
[umati wa watu wakiimba]
Feyd-Rautha! Feyd-Rautha!

01:19:42.182 --> 01:19:43.817
[Feyd-Rautha]
Mtumwa huyo hakulewa na dawa.

01:19:45.019 --> 01:19:46.153
[bofya ulimi]

01:19:46.186 --> 01:19:48.822
Ulijaribu kuniua.

01:19:48.856 --> 01:19:51.225
Asubuhi hii
ulikuwa mvulana wa kucheza,

01:19:51.258 --> 01:19:53.160
kuogopa na kuonewa wivu,

01:19:53.193 --> 01:19:56.497
lakini usiku wa leo wewe ni shujaa.

01:19:56.531 --> 01:19:58.265
Zawadi yangu kwako.

01:19:58.299 --> 01:20:00.301
Ninapaswa kukuzamisha
katika bonde hilo.

01:20:00.334 --> 01:20:01.835
[Baron Harkonnen anacheka]

01:20:01.869 --> 01:20:04.071
Usiwe na haraka.

01:20:04.104 --> 01:20:06.541
Nina zawadi nyingine kwa ajili yako.

01:20:06.574 --> 01:20:07.941
Kubwa zaidi.

01:20:09.443 --> 01:20:11.211
Arrakis.

01:20:11.245 --> 01:20:13.113
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

01:20:14.982 --> 01:20:16.850
Vipi kuhusu Rabban?

01:20:16.884 --> 01:20:19.153
[Baron Harkonnen] Ameshindwa
kulinda uzalishaji wa viungo.

01:20:19.186 --> 01:20:21.355
Rabban atapangiwa kazi nyingine.

01:20:23.957 --> 01:20:25.292
[anacheka]

01:20:25.326 --> 01:20:28.228
Tame Arrakis, Feyd.

01:20:28.262 --> 01:20:30.864
Bure viungo.
Nitakufanya kuwa Kaizari.

01:20:43.177 --> 01:20:45.012
[bofya ulimi] Mfalme?

01:20:48.215 --> 01:20:49.183
Jinsi gani?

01:20:51.318 --> 01:20:54.254
Mfalme alinisaidia
kuharibu Atreides.

01:20:55.590 --> 01:20:58.359
Alikopesha jeshi lake mwenyewe
kwa sababu.

01:20:58.392 --> 01:21:00.928
Uhalifu mkubwa.

01:21:00.961 --> 01:21:05.165
Ikiwa ilionekana,
Majumba Makuu yangeinuka
dhidi yake.

01:21:05.999 --> 01:21:07.201
Na kisha ...

01:21:08.469 --> 01:21:10.904
ni nani atakayeketi katika kiti cha enzi?

01:21:11.673 --> 01:21:14.908
Feyd-Rautha Harkonnen.

01:21:52.514 --> 01:21:53.480
[blade swishes]

01:21:55.149 --> 01:21:56.283
Unanifuata.

01:21:57.652 --> 01:21:58.686
Je! ni mimi?

01:22:00.655 --> 01:22:02.189
Huenda nimepotea.

01:22:04.358 --> 01:22:09.062
Je, utanionyesha njia
kutoka kwenye msukosuko huu,
Bwana wangu na-Baron?

01:22:16.303 --> 01:22:18.472
Tumekutana, sivyo?

01:22:21.743 --> 01:22:23.043
Sidhani hivyo.

01:22:24.011 --> 01:22:26.413
Mimi ni Lady Margot Fenring.

01:22:26.447 --> 01:22:28.750
Niko hapa kuheshimu
ujio wako wa uzee.

01:22:28.783 --> 01:22:30.552
Huruhusiwi
katika sehemu hii.

01:22:31.686 --> 01:22:33.287
Ulipataje
kupita walinzi?

01:22:33.320 --> 01:22:34.522
Walinzi?

01:22:37.491 --> 01:22:39.393
[imepotoshwa] naomba kuuliza,
unafanya nini hapa?

01:22:41.663 --> 01:22:45.098
Hushiriki
katika sherehe zako mwenyewe?

01:22:52.406 --> 01:22:54.174
[anapumua sana]

01:22:55.442 --> 01:22:58.278
[kutetemeka]
Wewe ni Bene Gesserit.

01:22:58.312 --> 01:23:01.181
[Lady Margot Fenring]
Na nini hufanya
unasema hivyo?

01:23:01.215 --> 01:23:03.685
[Feyd-Rautha] Nakumbuka sasa.

01:23:03.718 --> 01:23:06.420
Niliota juu yako jana usiku.

01:23:06.453 --> 01:23:08.155
[Lady Margot Fenring]
<i>Ndoto ya kupendeza,</i>
<i>Natumaini.</i>

01:23:08.188 --> 01:23:09.691
[Feyd-Rautha]
Usinidhihaki mwanamke.

01:23:09.724 --> 01:23:11.058
[Lady Margot Fenring]
<i>Nisingethubutu.</i>

01:23:13.393 --> 01:23:16.396
Najua yako
Mbinu za Bene Gesserit.

01:23:16.430 --> 01:23:18.700
Na unajua nini
kuhusu Bene Gesserit?

01:23:22.604 --> 01:23:23.470
Niambie.

01:23:27.709 --> 01:23:29.309
Kuna kitu kibaya?

01:23:29.343 --> 01:23:30.645
[Feyd-Rautha]
Sitambui mahali hapa.

01:23:31.846 --> 01:23:33.515
Huu ni mrengo wa wageni.

01:23:33.548 --> 01:23:36.350
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

01:23:36.383 --> 01:23:37.484
[Feyd-Rautha]
Unaenda wapi?

01:23:39.386 --> 01:23:40.354
Kwa chumba changu.

01:24:07.582 --> 01:24:13.053
[Lady Margot Fenring ananong'ona]
Njoo. Kwa. Mimi.

01:24:16.356 --> 01:24:17.457
Piga magoti.

01:24:20.695 --> 01:24:22.429
[anapumua sana]

01:24:31.606 --> 01:24:34.474
[Lady Margot Fenring ananong'ona]
Weka mkono wako wa kulia kwenye sanduku.

01:24:37.444 --> 01:24:39.814
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

01:24:49.691 --> 01:24:53.126
[Lady Margot Fenring]
Mwanasosholojia.
Mwenye akili ya juu.

01:24:53.160 --> 01:24:55.162
Inaendeshwa. Mkatili.

01:24:55.195 --> 01:24:57.264
Lakini kuhamasishwa sana
kwa heshima.

01:24:58.398 --> 01:25:00.535
Anatamani kuumizwa.

01:25:00.568 --> 01:25:02.502
Anapenda maumivu.

01:25:02.537 --> 01:25:04.137
[Mchungaji Mama Mohiam]
Je, anaweza kukombolewa?

01:25:04.171 --> 01:25:05.640
[Lady Margot Fenring]
Anaweza kudhibitiwa.

01:25:05.673 --> 01:25:07.441
Ana hatari ya ngono.

01:25:09.611 --> 01:25:10.477
Na?

01:25:11.946 --> 01:25:13.615
Mstari wa damu umewekwa salama.

01:25:15.382 --> 01:25:18.218
Mwanamke, kama ulivyoomba.

01:25:19.252 --> 01:25:21.589
Umefanya vizuri, Margot.

01:25:21.623 --> 01:25:24.826
Kwa heshima, kwa nini hukufanya
mjaribu mwenyewe?

01:25:26.293 --> 01:25:28.730
Mimi ni sura ya mama.

01:25:28.763 --> 01:25:32.366
Na kulingana na kile kilichotokea
kati yake na mama yake,

01:25:32.399 --> 01:25:34.936
sikutarajia
kuwa na ufanisi.

01:25:34.969 --> 01:25:36.571
Nini kilitokea kati ya
yeye na mama yake?

01:25:37.371 --> 01:25:38.238
Alimuua.

01:25:39.674 --> 01:25:42.644
Tamaa na unyonge.

01:25:43.911 --> 01:25:46.514
Hizo ndizo mbwembwe zake.

01:25:46.547 --> 01:25:48.916
Ikiwa Feyd-Rautha
inashinda Arrakis,

01:25:48.950 --> 01:25:51.653
tutajua
jinsi ya kumdhibiti.

01:25:53.387 --> 01:25:55.590
[wanaume wakisema]

01:26:04.231 --> 01:26:06.634
[Mtangazaji Mkuu wa Giedi
akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:26:10.838 --> 01:26:12.507
[anazungumza katika Harkonnen]

01:26:12.540 --> 01:26:14.842
Niondolee huyu Demu wa Fremen.

01:26:14.876 --> 01:26:17.545
[umati wa watu wakiimba]

01:26:22.850 --> 01:26:24.351
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

01:26:29.891 --> 01:26:33.493
[umati wa watu wakiimba]
Feyd-Rautha! Feyd-Rautha!

01:26:33.528 --> 01:26:37.832
Feyd-Rautha! Feyd-Rautha!

01:26:37.865 --> 01:26:39.534
Feyd-Rautha!

01:26:40.467 --> 01:26:43.838
[ngoma ikipigwa huisha]

01:26:47.675 --> 01:26:48.910
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

01:26:48.943 --> 01:26:51.244
[kuvuta pumzi]

01:26:52.013 --> 01:26:55.248
[kutetemeka kwa mashine]

01:26:58.820 --> 01:27:00.287
[Gurney akiimba]

01:27:00.320 --> 01:27:02.489
♪ <i>Achana na wajinga hawa ♪</i>

01:27:02.523 --> 01:27:05.392
♪ <i>Ninalaumu ♪</i>

01:27:05.425 --> 01:27:09.262
♪ <i>Suti yangu bado</i>
<i>Amejaa piss ♪</i>

01:27:10.631 --> 01:27:14.769
♪ <i>Mkono wangu umejaa mchanga ♪</i>

01:27:16.671 --> 01:27:18.940
♪ <i>Niokoe kutoka</i>
<i>Wapuuzi hawa wa ajabu ♪</i>

01:27:18.973 --> 01:27:22.810
♪ <i>Ulimwengu mwingine, ardhi nyingine ♪</i>

01:27:22.844 --> 01:27:23.745
[mtu 1] Tumeingia.

01:27:27.615 --> 01:27:28.850
[Gurney] Juicy?

01:27:28.883 --> 01:27:30.718
[mtu 1] Juicy, juicy.

01:27:30.752 --> 01:27:33.386
[kengele inalia]

01:27:33.420 --> 01:27:35.022
[mtu 1] Naam, ilikuwa nzuri
kukufahamu.

01:27:35.056 --> 01:27:36.557
[Gurney] Ah, ndio?

01:27:36.591 --> 01:27:38.325
Rada iko wazi. Tuko wazi.

01:27:39.727 --> 01:27:41.229
[Gurney] Wakati wa kupikia.

01:28:01.048 --> 01:28:02.817
Juicy, juicy.

01:28:02.850 --> 01:28:04.819
[mtu 2 kupitia comms]
Ndio, nilipata kusoma mita--

01:28:04.852 --> 01:28:06.854
[mtu 1 kupitia comms]
Sawa, wavulana,
minyoo wako njiani.

01:28:06.888 --> 01:28:07.955
[mtu 2] Jihadharini
kwa michubuko.
[mtu 1] Jitayarishe kuweka kizimbani.

01:28:07.989 --> 01:28:09.356
[mtu 2] Kutakuwa na joto.

01:28:13.493 --> 01:28:15.428
[mtu 1] Crank 'em up!
Watupe juu!

01:28:15.462 --> 01:28:17.031
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri juu ya maoni]

01:28:44.158 --> 01:28:45.092
[Gurney] Shikilia!

01:28:51.866 --> 01:28:53.568
[anapumua sana]

01:28:59.640 --> 01:29:01.008
Yangu! Yangu!

01:29:01.042 --> 01:29:02.777
[mtu 1] Songa!

01:29:02.810 --> 01:29:04.679
[kupiga kelele zisizo na maana]

01:29:06.814 --> 01:29:09.050
[mtu 1] Mashariki! Mashariki!
[mtu 2] Pata uwazi!

01:29:10.718 --> 01:29:11.686
[kuguna]

01:29:15.690 --> 01:29:17.625
[mtu 1] Hebu tuondoke hapa!

01:29:17.658 --> 01:29:19.026
[mtu 2] Inayoingia!

01:29:22.462 --> 01:29:24.098
[Gurney] Usikimbie, pigana!

01:29:25.900 --> 01:29:27.869
[mtu 1] Tuko ndani kabisa
Mambo ya Fremen.

01:29:29.937 --> 01:29:31.438
Mama Mtakatifu.

01:29:31.471 --> 01:29:33.373
[kupiga kelele zisizo na maana]

01:29:42.617 --> 01:29:43.751
[Gurney] Ah, jamani.

01:29:43.784 --> 01:29:45.786
[kupiga kelele zisizo na maana]

01:29:55.495 --> 01:29:56.731
[Gurney anaguna]

01:29:57.598 --> 01:29:58.833
[suruali nzito]

01:30:00.735 --> 01:30:03.571
[Paul] Nilitambua
nyayo zako...

01:30:03.604 --> 01:30:05.172
- mzee.
[Gurney ananong'ona] Hapana.

01:30:05.206 --> 01:30:06.741
[Paul anacheka]

01:30:06.774 --> 01:30:08.408
[Wapiganaji wa Fedaykin
wakipiga kelele huko Chakobsa]

01:30:12.747 --> 01:30:15.482
[wote wakilalamika]

01:30:21.555 --> 01:30:23.691
[amri ya kelele huko Chakobsa]

01:30:23.724 --> 01:30:25.760
[Wapiganaji wa Fedaykin
wakipiga kelele huko Chakobsa]

01:30:26.627 --> 01:30:27.628
[Paul anacheka]

01:30:27.662 --> 01:30:29.530
[kuhema]

01:30:29.563 --> 01:30:31.666
[Paul anacheka]
- Wewe mtoto mchanga.

01:30:32.233 --> 01:30:34.101
Wewe mtoto mdogo!

01:30:34.135 --> 01:30:38.139
[akihema kwa nguvu, anacheka]

01:30:41.175 --> 01:30:43.911
[Gurney] Mmm.
Baada ya Vita vya Arrakeen,

01:30:43.945 --> 01:30:47.447
Niliweza kujadili safari
kurudi nyumbani kwa waliookoka.

01:30:48.683 --> 01:30:50.718
Asante kwa hawa jamaa.

01:30:50.751 --> 01:30:51.953
[Paulo] Kwa nini ulikaa?

01:30:52.987 --> 01:30:54.454
Kweli, nilitaka damu.

01:30:56.657 --> 01:30:57.758
[Paulo] kichwa cha Rabban?

01:30:58.893 --> 01:31:00.861
Mm-hmm.

01:31:00.895 --> 01:31:03.998
Naam, tangu <i>Muad'Dib's</i>
umekuwa ukimfanya Rabban kuwa wazimu,

01:31:04.031 --> 01:31:08.903
biashara ya magendo
imekuwa na faida kubwa.

01:31:08.936 --> 01:31:10.738
Gurney Halleck mfanyabiashara haramu.

01:31:11.572 --> 01:31:12.873
[anacheka kwa upole]

01:31:12.907 --> 01:31:15.242
Paulo <i>Muad'Dib.</i>

01:31:15.276 --> 01:31:17.979
Nimesikia hadithi nyingi
kuhusu <i>Muad'Dib.</i>

01:31:19.080 --> 01:31:20.648
Hakuna hata mmoja wao mrembo.

01:31:21.882 --> 01:31:23.184
[ananong'ona] Unaona hofu?

01:31:24.986 --> 01:31:26.821
[Paulo] Wakati rasilimali zetu
ni mdogo...

01:31:29.623 --> 01:31:31.125
hofu ndiyo yote tuliyo nayo.

01:31:48.843 --> 01:31:50.311
Wanaume wangapi na wewe?

01:31:50.344 --> 01:31:52.546
- Mia mbili.
- Mia mbili?

01:31:52.580 --> 01:31:53.280
[shusha]

01:31:57.118 --> 01:32:00.054
Je, unatambua kile unachoweza
kufikia na wanaume 200?

01:32:01.355 --> 01:32:03.090
Wapiganaji wa ajabu.

01:32:03.124 --> 01:32:04.658
Duncan alisema hapo
walikuwa mamilioni yao.

01:32:04.692 --> 01:32:06.293
Katika Deep Kusini, ndiyo.

01:32:06.327 --> 01:32:08.763
Naam, unasubiri nini?

01:32:08.796 --> 01:32:11.999
Na maelfu ya watu hawa,
unaweza kuchukua udhibiti
ya sayari nzima.

01:32:12.033 --> 01:32:14.068
Ni ndoto ya baba yako.
Unaogopa nini?

01:32:14.101 --> 01:32:15.102
[Chani ananong'ona] Hey!

01:32:17.204 --> 01:32:18.906
Ibada, Gurney.

01:32:20.207 --> 01:32:21.542
Walikuwa marafiki.

01:32:23.177 --> 01:32:24.612
Sasa wao ni wafuasi.

01:32:24.645 --> 01:32:26.714
<i>Muad'Dib,</i> Mtume.

01:32:26.747 --> 01:32:28.682
Kwa nini hilo ni jambo baya?
Itumie.

01:32:28.716 --> 01:32:30.851
Si rahisi hivyo.

01:32:30.885 --> 01:32:33.687
Una uwezo wa kulipiza kisasi
baba yako,
na unaogopa kuitumia?

01:32:33.721 --> 01:32:35.723
Spice alifungua akili yangu, Gurney.

01:32:36.690 --> 01:32:38.025
Ninaweza kuona mambo.

01:32:40.027 --> 01:32:43.964
Nikienda Kusini, maono yangu yote
kusababisha hofu.

01:32:43.998 --> 01:32:47.301
Mabilioni ya maiti
waliotawanyika katika galaksi.

01:32:47.334 --> 01:32:48.836
Wote wanakufa kwa sababu yangu.

01:32:49.870 --> 01:32:51.005
Kwa sababu unapoteza udhibiti.

01:32:53.074 --> 01:32:54.141
Kwa sababu ninaipata.

01:32:59.246 --> 01:33:00.714
[mashine inasikika]

01:33:13.027 --> 01:33:14.195
Hayo ni maji mengi.

01:33:16.964 --> 01:33:18.299
Chani.

01:33:18.332 --> 01:33:20.034
Je! [anacheka]
Mwangalie, hana tumaini.

01:33:20.901 --> 01:33:21.836
Yeye ni familia.

01:33:23.037 --> 01:33:25.272
[kuzomea hewa]

01:33:25.306 --> 01:33:26.307
Kweli?

01:33:33.848 --> 01:33:36.984
[Fremen akicheka]

01:33:37.017 --> 01:33:38.786
[Shishakli akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:33:45.359 --> 01:33:47.061
[Chani akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:33:52.900 --> 01:33:54.335
[Gurney anapumua]

01:33:54.368 --> 01:33:56.871
Hakuna haja ya kuwa nabii
kuona nini mbele.

01:33:57.771 --> 01:33:58.739
[anapumua]

01:33:59.807 --> 01:34:01.142
Njia yako inaongoza kwenye vita.

01:34:02.910 --> 01:34:03.978
Unajua hilo.

01:34:06.380 --> 01:34:08.749
Kwa hivyo, vita vinakuja.

01:34:08.782 --> 01:34:12.353
Utafanya nini ukihisi
pumzi yake juu ya shingo yako?

01:34:12.386 --> 01:34:14.321
[anapumua sana]

01:34:16.090 --> 01:34:18.359
Ikiwa hutaki kuinua
jeshi kusini,

01:34:18.392 --> 01:34:20.027
bado unaweza kuwa na chaguo.

01:34:23.364 --> 01:34:24.398
Nguvu ya moto...

01:34:26.133 --> 01:34:27.801
ambayo huna.

01:34:29.970 --> 01:34:30.938
Na mimi hapa.

01:34:35.409 --> 01:34:37.945
Najua alipo baba yako
alificha atomiki za familia.

01:34:43.350 --> 01:34:46.153
[Paulo] Kila Nyumba inamiliki
silaha ya atomiki.

01:34:47.522 --> 01:34:49.456
Nilidhani yetu ilikuwa imepotea.

01:34:51.926 --> 01:34:54.295
Ni kubwa, Chani.
Inaweza kubadilisha kila kitu.

01:34:59.767 --> 01:35:02.937
Ningeweza kulenga mabomu
kwenye mashamba kuu ya viungo.

01:35:04.905 --> 01:35:08.108
Anayeweza kuharibu kitu
ina udhibiti wake halisi.

01:35:09.843 --> 01:35:11.278
Kwa hivyo, unaweza kuidhibiti
na sio sisi?

01:35:13.548 --> 01:35:15.349
Uliniahidi
hukutaka madaraka.

01:35:17.251 --> 01:35:19.253
Haijalishi nifanye nini,
bado huniamini.

01:35:19.286 --> 01:35:22.056
Maana wewe ni mgeni.
Kama rafiki yako.

01:35:24.391 --> 01:35:25.993
Mimi si mgeni.

01:35:33.801 --> 01:35:35.069
Sio kwangu.

01:35:35.102 --> 01:35:36.770
Lakini kwa jangwa, uko.

01:35:37.871 --> 01:35:39.873
Utii wangu ni kwako.

01:35:40.542 --> 01:35:41.942
Kwa Fremen.

01:35:41.976 --> 01:35:43.777
Ninafanya hivi kwa ajili yetu sote.

01:35:45.246 --> 01:35:46.113
Je, unaniamini?

01:35:54.855 --> 01:35:55.923
Nitazungumza na Stilgar.

01:36:04.031 --> 01:36:05.032
[Gurney] Huko.

01:36:09.270 --> 01:36:12.473
Iko chini kabisa
pua za kila mtu.

01:36:13.941 --> 01:36:15.209
Si wajanja.

01:36:15.242 --> 01:36:17.011
Hilo ndilo wazo.

01:36:17.044 --> 01:36:19.246
Hakuna mtu ambaye angeweza kutazama huko
kwa sababu ni dhahiri.

01:36:21.915 --> 01:36:23.884
-Si wajanja.
[kicheko]

01:36:23.917 --> 01:36:25.386
Je, umeipata?

01:36:25.419 --> 01:36:27.589
- Sikuitafuta.
[kicheko]

01:36:27.622 --> 01:36:29.089
Vichwa vingapi hasa?

01:36:30.958 --> 01:36:32.893
Kutosha kulipua
sayari nzima.

01:36:35.963 --> 01:36:37.331
Ni tamathali ya usemi.

01:36:39.233 --> 01:36:40.267
Unajua ninachomaanisha.

01:36:42.002 --> 01:36:43.538
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

01:36:45.973 --> 01:36:47.975
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

01:36:57.652 --> 01:36:59.253
[anapumua sana]

01:37:01.455 --> 01:37:02.990
[kuhema]

01:37:03.023 --> 01:37:04.958
[Gurney] Pekee na
urithi wako wa maumbile.

01:37:11.332 --> 01:37:14.335
[bofya]
[kufungua mlango]

01:37:18.339 --> 01:37:20.341
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

01:37:44.632 --> 01:37:48.335
[Gurney]
Wa babu wa babu yako
urithi.

01:37:48.369 --> 01:37:52.072
92 asili
Familia ya Atreides
vichwa vya atomiki.

01:37:55.008 --> 01:37:58.178
Sasa hiyo ndiyo nguvu.

01:38:05.052 --> 01:38:09.256
[Irulan]
Diary ya Imperial. Mwaka 10,191.

01:38:09.289 --> 01:38:11.559
Maoni ya nane.

01:38:11.593 --> 01:38:15.462
Taarifa kutoka
kusini mwa Arrakis
kufika mara chache.

01:38:15.496 --> 01:38:19.199
<i>Hizi ni ardhi tasa, zilizoteketea</i>
<i>iliyofichwa na dhoruba za mchanga</i>

01:38:19.233 --> 01:38:21.502
<i>ambayo inaenea maili elfu</i>
<i>ng'ambo ya ikweta.</i>

01:38:23.504 --> 01:38:27.441
<i>Hakuna kinachoweza kuishi huko</i>
<i>bila imani.</i>

01:38:27.474 --> 01:38:31.546
<i>Ambayo ni kwa nini</i>
<i>wamisionari wetu wa Bene Gesserit</i>
<i>zimekuwa na tija sana huko.</i>

01:38:35.082 --> 01:38:38.051
<i>Kupitia wao,</i>
<i>tunapokea ripoti</i>
<i>ya sura ya ajabu</i>

01:38:38.085 --> 01:38:39.953
<i>kuchukua mshiko</i>
<i>juu ya mawazo</i>

01:38:39.987 --> 01:38:43.357
<i>wa Kusini</i>
<i>makabila ya kimsingi.</i>

01:38:43.390 --> 01:38:47.027
<i>Mama Mchungaji mpya</i>
<i>kutoka Kaskazini...</i>

01:38:47.060 --> 01:38:51.165
<i>kueneza neno</i>
<i>ya kuwasili kwa karibu</i>
<i>ya</i> Lisan al-Gaib,

01:38:51.198 --> 01:38:54.268
<i>"Sauti</i>
<i>kutoka Ulimwengu wa Nje."</i>

01:38:54.301 --> 01:38:57.572
<i>Kwa bidii ya kidini</i>
<i>kupanda kusini,</i>

01:38:57.605 --> 01:39:01.408
<i>na</i> Muad'Dib
<i>kunyonga uzalishaji wa viungo</i>
<i>Kaskazini,</i>

01:39:01.442 --> 01:39:04.945
<i>kila kitu pointi</i>
<i>kwa kuongezeka kwa vita.</i>

01:39:12.052 --> 01:39:14.054
[mwanamke akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:39:24.699 --> 01:39:25.567
Hmm.

01:39:35.342 --> 01:39:36.210
Kimya.

01:39:49.122 --> 01:39:51.158
[muziki wa kusikitisha unacheza]

01:39:54.696 --> 01:39:55.697
[pigo]

01:39:57.732 --> 01:39:58.700
[pigo]

01:40:00.802 --> 01:40:02.102
[pigo]

01:40:03.671 --> 01:40:04.606
[pigo]

01:40:07.609 --> 01:40:09.511
[bofya ulimi]

01:40:09.544 --> 01:40:12.145
[mdudu analia]

01:40:12.179 --> 01:40:13.615
[bofya ulimi]

01:40:24.324 --> 01:40:25.225
[mdudu analia]

01:40:44.779 --> 01:40:47.715
[akizungumza kwa Chakobsa]

01:41:25.252 --> 01:41:26.854
Sikiliza kwa makini.

01:41:26.888 --> 01:41:28.590
Hivi karibuni mtu
atatembelea hekalu lako

01:41:28.623 --> 01:41:31.358
na anaweza kutaka
wewe kufanya ibada.

01:41:31.391 --> 01:41:34.328
Mama mchungaji,
ni haramu.

01:41:34.361 --> 01:41:36.229
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:41:39.667 --> 01:41:41.501
[kupotoshwa] Hebu ajaribu!

01:41:46.674 --> 01:41:48.676
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

01:41:52.580 --> 01:41:54.682
[Chani akihema]

01:41:58.318 --> 01:41:59.921
[sauti potofu ikiongea]

01:41:59.954 --> 01:42:02.456
[kuhema]

01:42:14.969 --> 01:42:15.870
[kushtuka]

01:42:15.903 --> 01:42:17.404
[milio ya bunduki kwa mbali]

01:42:21.743 --> 01:42:24.712
[kuhema]
[kupiga kelele zisizo dhahiri]

01:42:25.613 --> 01:42:26.781
Kuzimu nini?

01:42:30.384 --> 01:42:31.619
Chani!

01:42:32.887 --> 01:42:35.757
[kutetemeka kwa mashine]

01:42:37.592 --> 01:42:38.893
[kuhema]
[Paul] Chani!

01:42:42.964 --> 01:42:44.231
Chani.

01:42:44.264 --> 01:42:46.166
[wote wawili wakihema]

01:42:47.434 --> 01:42:50.872
[Fremen akipiga kelele bila kujulikana]

01:42:53.908 --> 01:42:55.610
Sietch Tabr.

01:42:55.643 --> 01:42:58.211
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

01:43:14.929 --> 01:43:17.264
[akiimba huko Harkonnen]

01:43:19.901 --> 01:43:21.602
[Baron Harkonnen]
Silaha za kizamani.

01:43:22.737 --> 01:43:24.672
Fikra.

01:43:24.706 --> 01:43:27.542
Kwa kweli tunayeyusha mwamba
juu ya vichwa vyao.

01:43:27.575 --> 01:43:30.611
Nataka kwenda ardhini.
Tayarisha askari wangu.

01:43:30.645 --> 01:43:33.815
Mola wangu Mlezi. Ningependekeza
ukae ndani.
Kulikuwa na-- [choki]

01:43:33.848 --> 01:43:35.783
Lete mwili wake mahali pangu.

01:43:35.817 --> 01:43:36.918
[kusonga]

01:43:36.951 --> 01:43:39.286
Maskini wapenzi wangu wana njaa.

01:43:39.319 --> 01:43:40.988
Hakukuwa na chakula
kwao kwenye ndege.

01:43:42.590 --> 01:43:45.026
[Rabban]
Unafanya nini hapa?

01:43:45.059 --> 01:43:48.295
Ni asubuhi na mapema.
Unafanya nini hapa?

01:43:48.328 --> 01:43:49.997
Busu miguu yangu, ndugu.

01:43:50.031 --> 01:43:51.298
Nitakufukuza --

01:43:51.331 --> 01:43:53.400
[Rabban anapiga kelele kwa uchungu, anaguna]

01:43:53.433 --> 01:43:54.936
[anapumua sana]

01:43:57.304 --> 01:43:59.774
[Feyd-Rautha]
Umeidhalilisha familia yetu.

01:44:00.908 --> 01:44:02.677
Umenidhalilisha.

01:44:03.678 --> 01:44:05.046
Busu...

01:44:05.079 --> 01:44:06.881
[miguno]
[Feyd-Rautha] au kufa.

01:44:11.953 --> 01:44:14.421
[busu, kuhema]

01:44:17.357 --> 01:44:18.458
Tuko hata sasa.

01:44:24.632 --> 01:44:27.267
[Baron Harkonnen]
Aibu familia yetu
mara moja zaidi...

01:44:28.536 --> 01:44:29.704
itakuwa ya mwisho.

01:44:30.905 --> 01:44:32.874
[muziki wa kuigiza unacheza]

01:44:46.788 --> 01:44:48.790
[mwanamke akipiga kelele]

01:44:51.993 --> 01:44:53.861
[kuzungumza bila kujulikana
huko Chakobsa]

01:44:59.499 --> 01:45:01.501
[mwanamke analia,
akizungumza katika Chakobsa]

01:45:04.672 --> 01:45:07.108
[Stilgar] Hawakufanya hata
kujihusisha ardhini,

01:45:07.141 --> 01:45:09.510
kama wapiganaji wa heshima.

01:45:09.544 --> 01:45:11.344
[Shishakli akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:45:11.378 --> 01:45:13.480
[mtu kwenye redio
akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:45:15.149 --> 01:45:16.717
[Shishakli akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:45:26.561 --> 01:45:27.662
[hupumua kwa nguvu]

01:45:29.630 --> 01:45:31.032
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

01:45:38.072 --> 01:45:41.809
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

01:45:41.843 --> 01:45:44.879
<i>Usul,</i> kusini...

01:45:44.912 --> 01:45:47.414
viongozi pekee
wanaruhusiwa kuongea.

01:45:48.716 --> 01:45:51.586
-Lazima uchukue nafasi yangu.
-Siwezi kufanya hivyo.

01:45:51.619 --> 01:45:54.522
Ni wakati mzuri
kuvuka blade pamoja nami.

01:45:54.555 --> 01:45:57.859
Mimi ni dhaifu.
Mimi ni muuaji rahisi, <i>Muad'Dib.</i>

01:45:57.892 --> 01:45:59.861
Afadhali nikate mkono wangu mwenyewe.

01:45:59.894 --> 01:46:02.630
Tunakuhitaji.
Tunahitaji <i>Lisan al-Gaib</i>
kuwaongoza watu wetu.

01:46:02.663 --> 01:46:04.599
Unajua ninachofikiria
ya yote hayo, Stilgar.

01:46:04.632 --> 01:46:07.034
Sijali unachoamini.
Ninaamini.

01:46:11.806 --> 01:46:13.507
[Muziki mkali unacheza]

01:46:16.544 --> 01:46:18.713
[kupiga kelele]

01:46:21.616 --> 01:46:22.884
Sikuiona ikija.

01:46:24.785 --> 01:46:26.520
The Harkonnens
hazifanyiki hapa.

01:46:27.622 --> 01:46:29.757
Walirudi tu kupakia tena.

01:46:29.790 --> 01:46:31.659
Tunaweka vishindo.

01:46:31.692 --> 01:46:33.027
Tunasonga kila mtu
kuelekea Kusini.

01:46:33.060 --> 01:46:34.962
Nitabaki nyuma
na kufunika mafungo yako.

01:46:34.996 --> 01:46:37.430
-Unazungumzia nini?
-Chani, siwezi kwenda nawe.

01:46:38.099 --> 01:46:39.700
Unajua kwa nini.

01:46:39.734 --> 01:46:41.736
[Gurney] nitabaki, pia.
- Hakuna anayebaki isipokuwa mimi.

01:46:41.769 --> 01:46:44.205
[Gurney] Paul.
- Hiyo ni amri,
Gurney Halleck! Nenda Kusini!

01:46:44.238 --> 01:46:45.606
Mlinde mama yangu.

01:46:48.042 --> 01:46:49.176
-Mola wangu.
[Shishakli] <i>Muad'Dib.</i>

01:46:49.210 --> 01:46:50.611
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:46:59.220 --> 01:47:01.055
Anaogopa
ya watu wenye msimamo mkali.

01:47:02.590 --> 01:47:03.591
Na anapaswa kuwa.

01:47:14.969 --> 01:47:17.004
[sauti za kale
kunong'ona bila kueleweka]

01:47:17.038 --> 01:47:18.438
[sauti ya kale 1] <i>Usipinge.</i>

01:47:23.144 --> 01:47:24.779
[kuunguruma potofu]

01:47:25.680 --> 01:47:27.148
Zungumza nami, Jamis.

01:47:31.953 --> 01:47:35.189
[sauti za kale
kunong'ona bila kueleweka]

01:47:38.025 --> 01:47:42.196
[sauti ya kale 2]
<i>Unaona vipande vipande tu.</i>

01:47:42.229 --> 01:47:46.167
<i>Huwezi kuona siku zijazo</i>
<i>bila kuona yaliyopita.</i>

01:47:48.536 --> 01:47:52.974
<i>Ili kufungua akili yako,</i>
<i>unahitaji kunywa</i>
<i>Maji ya Uzima...</i>

01:47:53.007 --> 01:47:55.943
<i>na utaona kila kitu.</i>

01:47:57.211 --> 01:47:59.613
[tetemeko]

01:47:59.647 --> 01:48:03.050
[Jamis] <i>Mwindaji mzuri</i>
<i>daima hupanda dune la juu zaidi</i>
<i>kabla ya kuwinda kwake.</i>

01:48:04.652 --> 01:48:05.820
<i>Anahitaji kuona ...</i>

01:48:07.788 --> 01:48:09.256
<i>kadiri anavyoweza kuona.</i>

01:48:14.662 --> 01:48:15.796
Unahitaji kuona.

01:48:18.666 --> 01:48:20.701
[Jessica] <i>Lazima unywe</i>
<i>Maji ya Uzima.</i>

01:48:22.003 --> 01:48:23.704
<i>Akili yako itafunguka,</i>

01:48:25.940 --> 01:48:27.641
<i>na utaona.</i>

01:48:46.027 --> 01:48:47.962
Dunia imefanya
chaguzi kwa ajili yetu.

01:48:53.067 --> 01:48:54.835
Nikienda Kusini,
Ninaweza kukupoteza.

01:48:54.869 --> 01:48:56.637
Hautawahi kunipoteza,

01:48:57.938 --> 01:48:59.106
Paul Atreides.

01:49:01.008 --> 01:49:03.310
Sio kwa muda mrefu
huku ukikaa vile ulivyo.

01:49:10.918 --> 01:49:12.920
Nitavuka
dhoruba na wewe.

01:49:12.953 --> 01:49:14.221
Nenda Kusini.

01:49:15.623 --> 01:49:17.091
Walete watu wako salama.

01:49:23.230 --> 01:49:25.933
Na kisha nitafanya
nini kifanyike.

01:49:34.775 --> 01:49:37.144
[kushangaza]
[kupiga kelele]

01:49:50.091 --> 01:49:51.258
Wapi?

01:49:51.292 --> 01:49:53.861
Jasusi. Kushoto nyuma.

01:49:53.894 --> 01:49:55.796
Hakuna athari ya wengine.

01:49:55.830 --> 01:49:58.299
[Feyd-Rautha]
Wamekwenda Kusini
kujificha katika dhoruba.

01:50:03.137 --> 01:50:04.872
Tuma ujumbe huu
kwa Baron.

01:50:04.905 --> 01:50:07.208
Kaskazini imekombolewa
na kulindwa.

01:50:07.241 --> 01:50:09.777
Vuna viungo kwa hiari yako.

01:50:09.810 --> 01:50:11.145
Ndiyo, na-Baron.

01:50:12.379 --> 01:50:13.714
[kamanda akizungumza Harkonnen]

01:50:25.893 --> 01:50:29.263
Uliua watu wangu tisa
na blade moja.

01:50:29.296 --> 01:50:30.798
[anadhihaki]

01:50:30.831 --> 01:50:32.666
[Mfasiri] Hatazungumza.

01:50:32.700 --> 01:50:34.668
[Feyd-Rautha]
Mwambie hiyo ni sawa.

01:50:34.702 --> 01:50:36.937
Mimi tayari kujua
kila kitu ninachohitaji kujua.

01:50:44.945 --> 01:50:46.780
Raha tu inabaki.

01:51:05.232 --> 01:51:07.234
[kuunguruma]

01:51:42.236 --> 01:51:44.104
[huzururaji]

01:51:54.248 --> 01:51:56.317
[Mtengenezaji Mlinzi
akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:52:41.596 --> 01:52:43.998
[sauti za kale
akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:52:52.139 --> 01:52:56.043
[sauti ya zamani]
<i>Sasa kwa kuwa unaweza kuona zamani zetu,</i>

01:52:59.313 --> 01:53:02.383
<i>unaweza kuona maisha yako ya baadaye.</i>

01:53:07.855 --> 01:53:11.792
[mawimbi yakipiga]

01:53:23.404 --> 01:53:27.274
[Alia] <i>Oh, ndugu,</i>
<i>kaka yangu mpendwa,</i>

01:53:27.308 --> 01:53:30.110
<i>hujajiandaa</i>
<i>kwa yatakayokuja.</i>

01:53:31.945 --> 01:53:35.249
<i>Sasa utajifunza ukweli</i>
<i>kuhusu familia yetu.</i>

01:53:35.282 --> 01:53:38.852
<i>Na itakuumiza</i>
<i>kwa msingi.</i>

01:53:40.387 --> 01:53:42.356
Paulo...

01:53:42.389 --> 01:53:45.459
<i>Usijali. niko na wewe.</i>

01:53:46.994 --> 01:53:48.362
nakupenda.

01:53:52.333 --> 01:53:54.101
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:53:58.505 --> 01:54:00.307
[mlinzi akizungumza]

01:54:01.509 --> 01:54:02.910
[imepotoshwa] Tafuta yao.

01:54:08.550 --> 01:54:11.251
[kupiga kelele]

01:54:25.399 --> 01:54:27.334
[kuhema]

01:54:28.402 --> 01:54:30.070
[manung'uniko ya watu huko Chakobsa]

01:54:31.338 --> 01:54:32.306
[kushtuka]

01:54:32.339 --> 01:54:33.340
[Chani] Paul?

01:54:34.108 --> 01:54:35.142
Paulo.

01:54:37.378 --> 01:54:39.980
niko hapa. niko hapa. Habari.

01:54:40.013 --> 01:54:41.048
[ anashusha pumzi polepole]

01:54:43.384 --> 01:54:44.652
[kwa kelele] Nini kilitokea?

01:54:46.220 --> 01:54:47.522
Nini kilitokea?

01:54:58.165 --> 01:54:59.701
Amekufa.

01:54:59.734 --> 01:55:02.469
Ishara zake muhimu ni za chini sana,
haziwezi kugunduliwa.

01:55:02.503 --> 01:55:03.971
Lakini yuko hai.

01:55:04.004 --> 01:55:05.506
Ulimfanya nini?

01:55:06.974 --> 01:55:09.076
Hapana, si hivyo.
Kwa nini angefanya hivyo?

01:55:09.109 --> 01:55:10.177
Kwa nini ungefanya hivyo?

01:55:10.210 --> 01:55:12.346
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:55:19.253 --> 01:55:22.657
Chani, mwili wake
anapigana na sumu
na anahitaji msaada wako.

01:55:22.690 --> 01:55:24.091
Wewe fanya hivyo.

01:55:25.259 --> 01:55:26.360
Ulimfanyia hivi.

01:55:26.393 --> 01:55:28.061
Ulifanya hivi
kwa mwanao!

01:55:28.095 --> 01:55:29.163
Wewe kufanya hivyo!

01:55:29.196 --> 01:55:31.198
Rekebisha mwenyewe.

01:55:31.231 --> 01:55:34.602
Chani, unaweza usiamini
katika unabii,
lakini wewe ni sehemu yake.

01:55:34.636 --> 01:55:36.336
[Chani] Wewe ndiye sumu.

01:55:36.370 --> 01:55:39.072
Wewe na uongo wako.
Kwa nini ungefanya hivi?

01:55:39.106 --> 01:55:40.274
[imepotoshwa] Fanya hivyo.

01:55:50.317 --> 01:55:52.486
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

01:56:03.598 --> 01:56:04.766
[crowd speaking Chakobsa]

01:56:04.799 --> 01:56:06.233
[minong'ono]
Machozi ya Jangwa la Spring.

01:56:30.525 --> 01:56:33.761
[sauti ya zamani]
<i>Kwisatz Haderach,</i>

01:56:33.795 --> 01:56:37.732
<i>kupanda juu. Inuka.</i>

01:56:37.765 --> 01:56:39.601
[kushtuka]

01:56:42.135 --> 01:56:43.170
[kushtuka]

01:56:44.304 --> 01:56:45.439
[anacheka]

01:56:47.407 --> 01:56:49.209
<i>Usul,</i> niko hapa. niko hapa.

01:56:52.747 --> 01:56:54.114
[anapumua]

01:56:55.282 --> 01:56:57.284
[manung'uniko ya watu]

01:56:58.553 --> 01:57:00.254
[Chani ananong'ona]
Uko sawa?

01:57:00.287 --> 01:57:01.288
Ndiyo.

01:57:07.427 --> 01:57:10.364
[Paul akipumua sana]

01:57:10.397 --> 01:57:11.533
Je, una uhakika?

01:57:11.566 --> 01:57:14.569
[kupumua sana]

01:57:15.603 --> 01:57:17.037
Asante kwako.

01:57:20.675 --> 01:57:21.743
[anapumua]

01:57:26.714 --> 01:57:28.616
[kupumua sana]

01:57:28.650 --> 01:57:29.651
[Chani anaguna]

01:58:02.684 --> 01:58:04.284
[Jessica]
Samahani kwa Chani.

01:58:05.787 --> 01:58:07.689
Atakuja kuelewa.

01:58:08.590 --> 01:58:09.824
Nimeiona.

01:58:11.458 --> 01:58:13.427
[ananong'ona] Unaweza kuona?

01:58:13.460 --> 01:58:15.730
Maono yako wazi sasa.

01:58:17.899 --> 01:58:21.703
Ninaona wakati ujao unaowezekana.
Wote mara moja.

01:58:22.870 --> 01:58:26.406
Adui zetu wametuzunguka pande zote.

01:58:26.440 --> 01:58:28.776
Na katika siku zijazo nyingi,
wanashinda.

01:58:29.711 --> 01:58:31.579
Lakini naona njia.

01:58:32.780 --> 01:58:35.182
Kuna njia nyembamba kupitia.

01:58:45.459 --> 01:58:47.294
Niliona damu yetu, Mama.

01:58:48.563 --> 01:58:49.897
Imeandikwa kwa wakati.

01:58:51.633 --> 01:58:53.635
[kupiga kelele]

01:59:02.577 --> 01:59:05.379
<i>Wewe ni binti</i>
<i>wa Baron Vladimir Harkonnen.</i>

01:59:08.281 --> 01:59:09.684
Baba yangu alijua?

01:59:15.723 --> 01:59:18.893
sikujijua,
mpaka nikachukua sumu ya mnyoo.

01:59:26.768 --> 01:59:28.402
Sisi ni Harkonnens.

01:59:30.872 --> 01:59:32.439
[anapumua]

01:59:32.472 --> 01:59:34.542
Kwa hivyo hivi ndivyo tutaweza kuishi.

01:59:36.309 --> 01:59:37.745
Kwa kuwa Harkonnens.

02:00:06.774 --> 02:00:10.310
[kugonga, kunguruma]

02:00:10.343 --> 02:00:12.847
[kubofya kwa kina]

02:01:02.362 --> 02:01:06.500
[mtu akiimba huko Chakobsa]

02:01:06.534 --> 02:01:11.539
[umati wa watu wakiimba]

02:01:11.572 --> 02:01:14.742
[mwanaume akiimba]

02:01:14.776 --> 02:01:15.810
Lazima tuzungumze.

02:01:17.845 --> 02:01:20.748
Stilgar, unaweza kuacha hii.
Je! unanisikia?

02:01:20.782 --> 02:01:22.482
Una nguvu
kusitisha hili.

02:01:22.517 --> 02:01:23.985
Mwanamke wa Kaskazini!

02:01:24.018 --> 02:01:25.887
Huruhusiwi
kuzungumza ndani ya duara.

02:01:25.920 --> 02:01:27.588
Ikiwa unataka kuzungumza,
unajua la kufanya.

02:01:27.622 --> 02:01:30.825
Stilgar, tafadhali.
Kwa ajili ya Arrakis.

02:01:32.560 --> 02:01:34.595
[mwanaume akiimba]

02:01:34.629 --> 02:01:35.730
[anadhihaki]

02:01:36.831 --> 02:01:40.668
[umati wa watu wakiimba]

02:01:40.701 --> 02:01:43.503
[manung'uniko ya watu]

02:01:43.538 --> 02:01:46.473
Unabii huu
ndivyo wanavyotufanya watumwa!

02:01:46.506 --> 02:01:48.609
Jinsi wanavyotawala-- [anaugulia]

02:01:48.643 --> 02:01:50.443
Utapata mwenyewe
katika shida.

02:01:50.477 --> 02:01:51.913
Hii hakuna
ya biashara yako.

02:01:51.946 --> 02:01:53.948
Rabban Harkonnen mwenyewe
aliua familia yangu.

02:01:53.981 --> 02:01:55.950
Alinipa kovu hili
kumkumbuka kwa.

02:01:55.983 --> 02:01:58.019
Hii ni biashara yangu yote.

02:01:58.052 --> 02:02:02.890
[pembe zinapiga]

02:02:02.924 --> 02:02:06.459
[manung'uniko ya watu]

02:02:24.579 --> 02:02:27.548
[manung'uniko yanazidi]

02:02:28.950 --> 02:02:31.586
[umati wa watu wakishangaa]

02:02:43.430 --> 02:02:44.999
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:02:45.032 --> 02:02:47.134
Viongozi wa kabila pekee ndio wanaoweza kuongea.

02:02:47.168 --> 02:02:49.469
Ukitaka
kushiriki sauti yako,

02:02:49.502 --> 02:02:52.439
lazima uchukue nafasi yake
kwa kumshinda

02:02:52.472 --> 02:02:54.876
na kurudisha maji yake
kisimani.

02:02:54.909 --> 02:02:58.478
Unadhani mimi ni mjinga vya kutosha
kujinyima mwenyewe
ya bora kati yetu?

02:02:59.146 --> 02:03:01.381
[Kelele huko Chakobsa]

02:03:02.717 --> 02:03:04.852
Chukua maisha yangu, <i>Usul.</i>

02:03:04.886 --> 02:03:06.921
Ni njia pekee.

02:03:06.954 --> 02:03:08.890
Ninaelekeza njia!

02:03:08.923 --> 02:03:11.058
[manung'uniko ya watu]

02:03:11.092 --> 02:03:12.627
[minong'ono] Polepole.

02:03:12.660 --> 02:03:15.395
[kupiga kelele huko Chakobsa]

02:03:18.633 --> 02:03:21.468
[makelele ya watu]

02:03:37.885 --> 02:03:39.587
[kimya]

02:03:48.195 --> 02:03:50.430
Lakini unafikiri
unaweza kuwa na nafasi.

02:03:52.700 --> 02:03:54.769
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:04:34.308 --> 02:04:35.943
Dune.

02:04:35.977 --> 02:04:37.611
<i>Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:04:37.645 --> 02:04:39.914
[umati wa watu wakiimba]
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:04:39.947 --> 02:04:41.182
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:04:41.215 --> 02:04:42.650
<i>Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:04:46.220 --> 02:04:47.722
[kupiga kelele huko Chakobsa]

02:04:53.828 --> 02:04:54.895
[kilio] <i>Muad'Dib!</i>

02:04:54.929 --> 02:04:56.797
[umati wa watu wakiimba] <i>Muad'Dib.</i>

02:04:59.233 --> 02:05:00.701
[anaugulia]

02:05:00.735 --> 02:05:01.769
[Stilgar akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:05:06.307 --> 02:05:08.075
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:05:08.109 --> 02:05:10.144
[umati wa watu wakishangaa]

02:05:21.155 --> 02:05:23.224
Hii ni ya baba yangu
saini ya pande mbili.

02:05:26.594 --> 02:05:27.695
[ anashusha pumzi polepole]

02:05:33.601 --> 02:05:36.203
[kupiga kelele] mimi ndiye
Paulo <i>Muad'Dib</i> Atreides,

02:05:36.237 --> 02:05:38.072
Duke wa Arrakis.

02:05:39.240 --> 02:05:41.108
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:05:47.348 --> 02:05:49.083
[ushangiliaji]
<i>-Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:05:49.116 --> 02:05:51.218
[umati wa watu wakiimba]
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:05:51.252 --> 02:05:55.589
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:05:55.623 --> 02:05:58.325
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:05:58.359 --> 02:06:01.328
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:06:01.362 --> 02:06:04.632
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:06:04.665 --> 02:06:07.835
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:06:07.868 --> 02:06:09.303
<i>Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:06:20.981 --> 02:06:22.083
[anapumua kwa kina]

02:06:46.841 --> 02:06:49.110
[Irulan]
Paul Atreides
bado yuko hai.

02:06:50.878 --> 02:06:52.379
Anampa changamoto baba yangu.

02:06:53.848 --> 02:06:55.616
Hujawahi kuwa
juu ya Arrakis.

02:06:57.084 --> 02:06:59.086
Inavutia sana.
Utaona.

02:06:59.120 --> 02:07:00.721
Haya yote yalikuwa
ushauri wako?

02:07:00.754 --> 02:07:02.790
Je!

02:07:02.823 --> 02:07:05.860
Ulimshauri baba yangu
kuwaangamiza Atreides?

02:07:05.893 --> 02:07:09.230
Bila shaka nilifanya. Kwa nini kingine
ingetokea?

02:07:09.263 --> 02:07:11.699
Ulijaribu kujitolea
damu nzima.

02:07:11.732 --> 02:07:13.801
Na nilikuwa sahihi
kuifanya.

02:07:13.834 --> 02:07:16.971
The <i>Kwisatz Haderach</i>
ni aina ya nguvu

02:07:17.004 --> 02:07:19.240
kwamba ulimwengu wetu
bado hajaona.

02:07:19.273 --> 02:07:21.876
Nguvu ya mwisho.

02:07:21.909 --> 02:07:23.744
Kwa vizazi tisini,

02:07:23.777 --> 02:07:25.813
tumesimamia
Nyumba ya Atreides.

02:07:25.846 --> 02:07:28.916
Walikuwa wakiahidi,
lakini walikuwa wanakuwa
hatari dharau.

02:07:28.949 --> 02:07:32.386
Damu yao
ilibidi kusitishwa.

02:07:32.419 --> 02:07:34.889
Ndio maana tumeweka
damu nyingi kazini.

02:07:34.922 --> 02:07:35.956
Matarajio kadhaa.

02:07:35.990 --> 02:07:37.424
Lakini imerudishwa nyuma.

02:07:37.458 --> 02:07:39.160
Paulo yu hai.

02:07:39.193 --> 02:07:41.128
Na kama
anamshinda Feyd-Rautha,
baba yangu--

02:07:41.162 --> 02:07:45.366
Baba yako
atapoteza kiti cha enzi
haijalishi nani atashinda.

02:07:45.399 --> 02:07:48.402
Lakini kuna njia moja
familia yako inaweza kubaki
madarakani

02:07:48.435 --> 02:07:51.872
na kupitia wewe,
muendelezo
ya uwakili wetu.

02:07:52.973 --> 02:07:54.842
Moja. Njia.

02:07:55.442 --> 02:07:57.945
Je, umejiandaa?

02:07:57.978 --> 02:08:00.681
Umekuwa ukinitayarisha
maisha yangu yote,
Mama Mchungaji.

02:08:02.983 --> 02:08:05.286
Unaelekea kaskazini
na wengine?

02:08:05.319 --> 02:08:07.254
Mimi ni Fedaykin.

02:08:07.288 --> 02:08:09.990
Nawafuata viongozi wangu.
Ikiwa mapigano yataenda kaskazini,
Ninakwenda kaskazini.

02:08:10.024 --> 02:08:11.392
Paulo hakuwa nayo
chaguo, Chani.

02:08:11.425 --> 02:08:14.061
Sitampigania.

02:08:14.094 --> 02:08:15.396
Ninapigania watu wangu.

02:08:19.266 --> 02:08:21.101
Nimekuja kukutakia
bora ya bahati.

02:08:22.369 --> 02:08:23.938
Napenda kukutakia vivyo hivyo,

02:08:25.906 --> 02:08:27.474
lakini inaonekana
umeshinda vita yako.

02:08:40.154 --> 02:08:42.156
[kushangaza]

02:08:50.798 --> 02:08:52.099
[Gurney] Alichukua chambo.

02:08:58.839 --> 02:09:00.774
[Paulo] Oh, maliki
kulazimishwa sana.

02:09:01.809 --> 02:09:03.377
Yeye ni sahihi kwa wakati.

02:09:04.345 --> 02:09:06.380
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:09:24.965 --> 02:09:27.067
[kushangaza]

02:09:36.477 --> 02:09:38.846
Anafanya nini hapa?

02:09:38.879 --> 02:09:40.981
Nilileta uzalishaji wa viungo
chini ya udhibiti.

02:09:44.151 --> 02:09:45.319
Tunafanya nini?

02:09:46.887 --> 02:09:49.591
Tuma ujumbe
kwa Nyumba Kubwa.

02:09:49.624 --> 02:09:53.861
Waambie kwamba Arrakis
iko chini ya shambulio la Sardakar.

02:09:53.894 --> 02:09:56.564
Waambie, maisha yao ya baadaye
hutegemea kwenye mizani.

02:10:20.487 --> 02:10:22.423
[kunong'ona kwa Chakobsa]

02:10:23.924 --> 02:10:26.427
[Paulo] Wakati dhoruba
hupiga mwamba huu,

02:10:26.460 --> 02:10:28.929
Gurney itafungua
njia kwako, Stilgar,

02:10:28.962 --> 02:10:31.231
ili uweze kuingia
bonde kutoka Magharibi

02:10:31.265 --> 02:10:33.601
na kuvuruga
mifumo yao ya ulinzi.

02:10:33.635 --> 02:10:35.436
Chani, nataka wewe
na Fedaykin yako

02:10:35.469 --> 02:10:36.970
kisha kushambulia
kutoka Mashariki,

02:10:37.938 --> 02:10:39.973
ndani ya bonde.

02:10:40.007 --> 02:10:42.109
Nitapiga
kutoka Kaskazini,
kichwa juu,

02:10:42.142 --> 02:10:44.211
pamoja na askari wa Kifundamentalisti.

02:10:44.244 --> 02:10:47.081
Nami nitatumikia Arrakeen
kwa dessert.

02:10:47.114 --> 02:10:49.283
Kumbuka,
Nahitaji Mfalme akiwa hai.

02:10:50.250 --> 02:10:52.486
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:10:52.520 --> 02:10:55.189
[yote kurudia]

02:10:57.024 --> 02:10:59.360
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

02:11:16.276 --> 02:11:19.279
[kupiga kelele, kuzomea]

02:11:27.655 --> 02:11:29.390
[kuunguruma kwa mashine, kuzomea]

02:11:43.337 --> 02:11:45.640
[kuunguruma kwa mashine, kuzomea]

02:11:49.544 --> 02:11:50.545
Hm.

02:11:53.313 --> 02:11:55.583
[kupumua sana]

02:11:58.686 --> 02:12:01.188
[Mfalme] Baron,

02:12:01.221 --> 02:12:06.059
una wazo lolote
nani huyu <i>Muad'Dib</i> inaweza kuwa?

02:12:06.093 --> 02:12:09.062
Mshupavu fulani, Mtukufu.
Hiyo ndiyo tu tunayojua.

02:12:09.096 --> 02:12:11.098
Zaidi. Zaidi. Nipe zaidi.

02:12:11.131 --> 02:12:12.232
Ni mwendawazimu!

02:12:12.266 --> 02:12:14.268
- Wazimu?
-Wote Fremen ni wazimu.

02:12:16.638 --> 02:12:18.673
[kudhihaki]
Hiyo ndiyo yote unayojua?

02:12:18.706 --> 02:12:20.675
Kweli?

02:12:20.708 --> 02:12:22.443
[Feyd-Rautha]
<i>Muad'Dib</i> amekufa.

02:12:24.746 --> 02:12:27.749
Au alijificha
katika dhoruba za Kusini

02:12:27.782 --> 02:12:29.450
ambayo ina maana sawa.

02:12:29.483 --> 02:12:30.417
[kutia saini]

02:12:30.451 --> 02:12:31.753
[Bashar] Mfalme wako,

02:12:31.786 --> 02:12:33.320
dhoruba ya mchanga
hiyo inakaribia

02:12:33.353 --> 02:12:35.757
inatishia uadilifu
ya ngao zetu.

02:12:35.790 --> 02:12:37.991
Tunapendekeza
kurudi kwenye obiti.

02:12:38.025 --> 02:12:39.993
Naam, milima
itatulinda
kutoka kwa wengi wake,

02:12:41.028 --> 02:12:42.229
Mtukufu.

02:12:44.031 --> 02:12:48.168
Baron, na wewe
iliyowahi kuchunguzwa

02:12:48.202 --> 02:12:51.539
mikoa ya kusini
ya Arrakis?

02:12:51.573 --> 02:12:54.274
Naam, mkoa mzima
haikaliki.

02:12:54.308 --> 02:12:57.010
Inajulikana sana,
Mtukufu.

02:12:57.044 --> 02:13:01.148
[Mfalme]
Kusini yako isiyokaliwa

02:13:01.181 --> 02:13:04.251
inaonyesha ushahidi
ya shughuli za binadamu.

02:13:04.284 --> 02:13:06.588
[Baron]
Sikuwa na ufahamu wa hili.

02:13:06.621 --> 02:13:09.156
nakuapia,
Sikuwa na ufahamu
yoyote kati ya haya.

02:13:09.189 --> 02:13:10.625
[Baron akihema]

02:13:10.658 --> 02:13:12.527
[anaugulia]
[kupumua]

02:13:14.161 --> 02:13:15.597
[Mfalme] <i>Muad'Dib</i> yuko hai.

02:13:17.064 --> 02:13:18.265
Lazima nimpate.

02:13:23.370 --> 02:13:26.574
[kupumua sana]

02:13:27.407 --> 02:13:29.409
[bendera zinapepea]

02:13:39.386 --> 02:13:41.388
[kushangaza]

02:13:44.458 --> 02:13:48.763
[kupiga, kubofya]

02:14:18.793 --> 02:14:22.797
[umati ukishangilia]

02:14:33.173 --> 02:14:35.510
[kupiga kelele huko Chakobsa]

02:14:35.543 --> 02:14:37.679
[umati unarudia kwa pamoja]

02:14:38.713 --> 02:14:40.213
Moto!

02:14:47.187 --> 02:14:48.690
[makombora yakiruka]

02:14:50.490 --> 02:14:53.427
[milipuko]

02:14:53.460 --> 02:14:57.865
[kuunguruma]

02:15:00.568 --> 02:15:01.803
[kuanguka]

02:15:15.550 --> 02:15:17.752
[kupiga kelele]
[Irulan akihema]

02:15:17.785 --> 02:15:19.854
[kuanguka]

02:15:19.887 --> 02:15:22.356
[Bashar]
Sardaukar! Kwa ulinzi!

02:15:22.389 --> 02:15:23.791
[Baron anaugua]

02:15:23.825 --> 02:15:26.894
[metal creaking]

02:15:32.734 --> 02:15:35.803
[kuanguka kwa mbali]

02:15:35.837 --> 02:15:38.573
[huzururaji]

02:15:38.606 --> 02:15:40.608
[kuporomoka]

02:15:55.322 --> 02:15:57.525
[blades unsheathe]

02:16:00.460 --> 02:16:03.397
[kupumua sana]

02:16:05.600 --> 02:16:07.902
[upepo unavuma]

02:16:09.771 --> 02:16:11.471
[afisa anapiga kelele
huko Galach]

02:16:16.778 --> 02:16:18.780
[kushangaza]

02:16:23.851 --> 02:16:25.920
[askari wakihema]
[blades unsheathe]

02:16:30.925 --> 02:16:34.326
[kutetemeka, kubofya kwa kina]

02:16:39.867 --> 02:16:43.771
[kuinama]

02:16:43.805 --> 02:16:46.406
[Sardakar akipiga kelele]

02:16:52.279 --> 02:16:57.718
[Fremen akipiga kelele]

02:17:10.531 --> 02:17:11.733
[Stilgar anaongea Chakobsa]

02:17:11.766 --> 02:17:13.366
[Wapiganaji wa Fremen
piga kelele kwa Chakobsa]

02:17:21.541 --> 02:17:24.611
[kupiga kelele kwa hofu]

02:17:33.821 --> 02:17:35.623
[kupiga kelele kwa hofu]

02:17:37.725 --> 02:17:39.660
[Wapiganaji wa Fremen
akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:17:51.004 --> 02:17:53.875
[Wapiganaji wa Fremen wanapiga kelele]

02:18:02.850 --> 02:18:04.316
[Chani anaongea Chakobsa]

02:18:04.351 --> 02:18:06.386
[Wapiganaji wa Fedaykin
akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:18:09.523 --> 02:18:12.527
[wote wakipiga kelele]

02:18:20.834 --> 02:18:22.468
[Chani akiguna]

02:18:49.831 --> 02:18:50.832
[askari wanaguna]

02:18:59.807 --> 02:19:02.843
[Baron akihema]

02:19:22.697 --> 02:19:24.031
[mlio mkubwa]

02:19:28.636 --> 02:19:30.437
[mlio mkubwa]

02:19:30.469 --> 02:19:32.504
[askari wanapiga kelele]

02:19:36.110 --> 02:19:37.111
[Bashar anapiga kelele] Sardakar!

02:20:42.610 --> 02:20:43.978
Babu.

02:21:06.100 --> 02:21:07.702
Unakufa kama mnyama.

02:21:38.933 --> 02:21:39.967
<i>Muad'Dib.</i>

02:21:41.035 --> 02:21:42.603
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:21:52.680 --> 02:21:54.548
[anapumua sana]

02:22:01.055 --> 02:22:02.556
[Kiongozi wa Fedaykin
akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:22:02.590 --> 02:22:06.727
[Wapiganaji wa Fremen
wakiimba huko Chakobsa]

02:22:23.778 --> 02:22:26.547
[askari wote wakipiga kelele]

02:22:37.758 --> 02:22:40.628
[kuguna]

02:23:09.657 --> 02:23:10.758
[Gurney] Rabban!

02:23:21.869 --> 02:23:23.637
Tazama ni nani amerudi kutoka kwa wafu.

02:23:29.777 --> 02:23:32.146
[kuguna]

02:23:34.148 --> 02:23:35.116
[kusonga]

02:23:35.850 --> 02:23:36.851
[kuhema]

02:23:37.985 --> 02:23:41.322
Kwa Duke wangu, na marafiki zangu.

02:24:18.392 --> 02:24:20.394
[mazungumzo yasiyo dhahiri]

02:24:31.372 --> 02:24:32.673
[Chani anaongea Chakobsa]

02:24:46.954 --> 02:24:47.988
[Stilgar] Meli za kivita.

02:24:50.324 --> 02:24:51.425
Nyumba Kubwa.

02:24:52.993 --> 02:24:55.462
Gurney, ni wakati.
Walete wafungwa.

02:24:55.496 --> 02:24:59.099
-Mola wangu.
[Stilgar anaongea Chakobsa]

02:24:59.133 --> 02:25:01.735
[anaongea Chakobsa]

02:25:06.340 --> 02:25:07.841
[anaongea Chakobsa]

02:25:22.957 --> 02:25:24.124
Hii bado haijaisha.

02:25:30.130 --> 02:25:31.365
Nataka ujue...

02:25:34.301 --> 02:25:36.303
nitakupenda
ilimradi nipumue.

02:25:39.039 --> 02:25:40.274
[anapumua]

02:25:40.307 --> 02:25:41.909
[mlango unafunguliwa]

02:25:41.942 --> 02:25:43.210
[anapumua kwa kina]

02:25:48.516 --> 02:25:50.985
Kuna armada ya wingi
katika obiti.

02:25:54.388 --> 02:25:58.158
Unakabiliwa
uvamizi kamili, Fremen.

02:25:58.192 --> 02:26:01.295
[Paulo] Unawezaje
kuwa na uhakika Nyumba kubwa
wako hapa kwa ajili yangu?

02:26:07.268 --> 02:26:11.573
Wanaweza kuwa na udadisi
kusikia upande wangu wa hadithi,
hufikirii?

02:26:11.606 --> 02:26:16.176
Mimi ni Paul Atreides,
mwana wa Leto Atreides,
Duke wa Arrakis.

02:26:18.012 --> 02:26:19.480
-Gurney.
-Mola wangu.

02:26:19.514 --> 02:26:21.882
Tuma onyo kwa meli zote.

02:26:21.915 --> 02:26:25.853
Ikiwa Nyumba Kubwa zitashambulia,
atomiki zetu zitatoweka
mashamba yote ya viungo.

02:26:27.354 --> 02:26:30.057
-Umerukwa na akili.
- Yeye ni bluffing.

02:26:30.090 --> 02:26:32.159
Fikiria jinsi ulivyo
Kuhusu kufanya, Paul Atreides.

02:26:32.192 --> 02:26:34.395
[kupotoshwa] Kimya!
[Mchungaji Mama Mohiam anashangaa]

02:26:34.428 --> 02:26:35.496
[kutetemeka]

02:26:36.564 --> 02:26:38.065
[kunong'ona] Chukizo.

02:26:42.303 --> 02:26:43.871
Ujumbe umetumwa, Bwana wangu.

02:26:45.906 --> 02:26:49.476
Kama mtumishi wa Imperium,
utainama miguuni pangu.

02:26:49.511 --> 02:26:53.113
Miguu yako? Utakuwa na bahati
kuweka kichwa chako.

02:26:56.350 --> 02:26:57.985
Nitachukua mkono
ya binti yako.

02:27:00.487 --> 02:27:02.489
Atabaki salama.

02:27:02.524 --> 02:27:05.159
Na tutatawala pamoja
juu ya Dola.

02:27:05.192 --> 02:27:07.494
[mazungumzo ya watu]
[anapumua sana]

02:27:14.935 --> 02:27:16.170
[Paulo] Lakini wewe...

02:27:19.039 --> 02:27:20.608
Unapaswa kujibu
kwa baba yangu.

02:27:28.248 --> 02:27:31.985
Unajua kwanini nilimuua?

02:27:33.253 --> 02:27:35.222
Kwa sababu alikuwa mwanaume

02:27:35.255 --> 02:27:37.224
walioamini
katika kanuni za moyo.

02:27:38.593 --> 02:27:40.494
Lakini moyo
sio maana ya kutawala.

02:27:42.096 --> 02:27:43.130
Kwa maneno mengine...

02:27:45.533 --> 02:27:49.203
baba yako alikuwa mtu dhaifu.

02:27:58.278 --> 02:28:01.315
Simama au chagua bingwa wako.

02:28:04.151 --> 02:28:05.587
[Feyd-Rautha]
Niko hapa, Atreides.

02:28:08.155 --> 02:28:09.390
Nahitaji blade.

02:28:09.423 --> 02:28:11.058
Kubali yangu.

02:28:23.070 --> 02:28:26.073
Usichafue mikono yako
juu ya mnyama huyu.

02:28:26.106 --> 02:28:27.441
Ngoja nishughulike naye.

02:28:27.474 --> 02:28:29.209
Ni mzigo wangu, Gurney.

02:28:43.691 --> 02:28:45.092
[Feyd-Rautha anapumua]

02:28:47.729 --> 02:28:50.230
Kwa nini anajihatarisha hivyo?

02:28:50.264 --> 02:28:52.567
<i>Muad'Dib</i> inaongoza njia.

02:28:54.334 --> 02:28:55.936
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:29:16.423 --> 02:29:19.727
Nina furaha
hatimaye kukutana nawe, binamu.

02:29:21.161 --> 02:29:23.997
Binamu? Je, hiyo ni sawa?

02:29:26.266 --> 02:29:31.171
Naam, haungekuwa
jamaa wa kwanza nimemuua.

02:29:33.775 --> 02:29:36.611
Na kisu chako kikate na kupasuka.

02:29:40.047 --> 02:29:44.184
[anacheka kwa upole]
Na kisu chako kikate na kupasuka.

02:29:47.354 --> 02:29:50.357
[wote wawili wakiguna]

02:30:24.626 --> 02:30:25.627
[matatizo ya watu]

02:30:26.326 --> 02:30:28.462
[kuhema]

02:30:35.202 --> 02:30:38.038
-Yeye ni kipenzi chako?
[anapumua sana]

02:30:52.820 --> 02:30:56.189
Tahadhari yoyote maalum
kwa kipenzi?

02:30:56.891 --> 02:30:58.760
[anapumua sana]

02:31:14.676 --> 02:31:16.109
[wote wawili wakiguna]

02:31:22.750 --> 02:31:23.785
[matatizo ya watu]

02:31:23.818 --> 02:31:25.118
[Feyd-Rautha anapiga kelele]

02:31:26.921 --> 02:31:28.121
[Paulo anaguna]

02:31:29.691 --> 02:31:31.859
[Paulo akiguna, akihema]

02:31:37.532 --> 02:31:38.733
[kuhema]

02:31:51.211 --> 02:31:52.346
[kuguna]

02:32:00.955 --> 02:32:02.824
[Feyd-Rautha anaguna]
[Paul akihema]

02:32:11.899 --> 02:32:14.334
[wote wawili wakiguna, wakihema]

02:32:22.910 --> 02:32:24.812
Umepigana vyema, Atreides.

02:32:26.213 --> 02:32:27.447
[kuhema]

02:32:28.750 --> 02:32:29.884
[Paulo anapiga kelele]

02:32:32.553 --> 02:32:34.221
<i>Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:32:34.254 --> 02:32:36.490
[Fremen wakiimba]
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:32:37.424 --> 02:32:38.526
[anapumua]

02:32:54.575 --> 02:32:56.577
[kuhema]

02:33:00.581 --> 02:33:01.649
[Paulo akiugulia]

02:33:03.483 --> 02:33:04.519
[kupiga kelele]

02:33:29.010 --> 02:33:31.713
[Jessica]
<i>Ulipaswa kuamini.</i>

02:33:31.746 --> 02:33:33.380
<i>Umechagua upande usiofaa.</i>

02:33:34.682 --> 02:33:36.349
[Mchungaji Mama Mohiam] <i>Upande?</i>

02:33:36.383 --> 02:33:39.453
<i>Wewe, kati ya watu wote,</i>
<i>wanapaswa kujua.</i>

02:33:39.486 --> 02:33:43.858
<i>Hakuna pande...</i>
<i>Mama Mchungaji.</i>

02:34:03.044 --> 02:34:04.946
Deni la maisha limelipwa.

02:34:04.979 --> 02:34:06.814
Acha baba yangu sasa
nami nitakuwa
bibi arusi wako tayari.

02:34:06.848 --> 02:34:08.381
Kiti cha enzi kitakuwa chako.

02:34:09.517 --> 02:34:11.753
[anapumua sana]

02:34:33.608 --> 02:34:34.642
[magongo]

02:35:16.449 --> 02:35:17.752
[kuvuta pumzi kwa kina]

02:35:40.942 --> 02:35:44.512
Mola wangu Mlezi,
Nyumba Kubwa zimejibu.

02:35:44.545 --> 02:35:46.446
Wanakataa
kuheshimu ukuu wako.

02:35:47.949 --> 02:35:51.085
Tunasubiri maagizo yako,
<i>Lisan al-Gaib.</i>

02:36:00.161 --> 02:36:01.996
Waongoze kwenye Pepo.

02:36:02.029 --> 02:36:03.698
[Fremen wa kike] <i>Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:36:03.731 --> 02:36:05.967
[wote wakiimba]
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:36:15.977 --> 02:36:20.915
[akizungumza Chakobsa]

02:36:20.948 --> 02:36:24.619
[wote wakiimba]
<i>Lisan al-Gaib! Lisan al-Gaib!</i>

02:36:33.160 --> 02:36:34.962
[Alia]
<i>Nini kinatokea, Mama?</i>

02:36:37.031 --> 02:36:39.533
Ndugu yako anashambulia
Nyumba Kubwa.

02:36:43.070 --> 02:36:45.505
Vita Takatifu huanza.

02:37:29.050 --> 02:37:31.052
[kupumua sana]